(3, 'The Apurva Kempinski', 'DwYDSP55ndP9zvonhCNMAWvSno', 'Nusa Dua', 'Jl. Raya Nusa Dua Selatan, Benoa, Kec. Kuta Sel., Kabupaten Badung, Bali', 'Dewi Sartika', '03612092288', '<p>Standing atop the majestic cliff of Nusa Dua, with breathtaking views of the Indian Ocean and tropical garden, The Apurva Kempinski Bali offers the epitome of beachfront luxury. This five-star hotel in Bali presents itself as a majestic open-air theatre, an embodiment of Indonesian elegance.</p><p>A collection of 475 iconic rooms, suites and villas are showcased, with 60% of the accommodation featuring its own private plunge pools. From a unique culinary journey and indigenous spa treatments, to the spacious meeting rooms and alluring chapels, The Apurva Kempinski Bali is a spectacular stage where curated experiences are brought to life.</p>', '<ul><li>High-Speed Internet Access</li><li>Experiential Concierge</li><li>Lady In Red</li><li>Swimming Pool and Kids Pool</li><li>Cliff Lounge</li><li>Villa Lounge</li><li>Asha Curated Boutique &amp; Gallery</li><li>Jalak Family Club</li><li>In-Room Dining</li><li>Idyllic Beach</li><li>Business Centre</li><li>Parking &amp; Valet</li><li>Airport Pick-Up Service</li></ul>', '<p><b>Standard Benefit :</b><br />Daily breakfast</p><p><b>Children Policy :</b></p><ul><li>Children 0-5 years old share their parent&#39;s room at no extra charge</li><li>Babycot is complimentary</li><li>Breakfast is complimentary for children under 6 years old</li></ul><p><b>Honeymoon Benefit (Min 2 night stay) :</b><br />Welcome drink, nice petal flowers of in-room arrangement, variety of in-room fruit bowl, honeymooner&rsquo;s cake and romantic turn down service amenities on day of arrival.</p><p><b>Seasonal Policy :</b><br />No check out is allowed on 31 Dec 2023</p>', 'Active', '1682560259_the-apurva-kempinski-bali_grand-staircase.jpg', 14, 'https://www.kempinski.com/en/bali/the-apurva-kempinski-bali/dining/', 'https://g.page/KempinskiBali?share', NULL, NULL, '<p><strong>Normal Season</strong> (01 April &ndash; 14 July 2023, 01 Sep &ndash; 20 Dec&rsquo;2023, 08 Jan &ndash; 31 March&rsquo;2024) :&nbsp;</p><ul><li>Cancellation within 7 days prior to arrival : 1 night charge</li><li>Reduce in length of stay within 7 days : 1 night charge</li><li>No show : 100% charge</li></ul><p><strong>High Season</strong> (15 July &ndash; 31 Aug 2023, 21 &ndash; 26 Dec 2023) : <b><u> </u></b></p><ul><li>Cancellation within 8 to 14 days prior to arrival : 1 night charge</li><li>Cancellation within 7 days or Early Departure / No Show : 100% charge</li></ul><p><strong>Peak Season</strong> (27 Dec 2023 &ndash; 07 Jan 2024) :</p><ul><li>Cancellation within 30 days prior to arrival : 1 night charge</li><li>Cancellation within 21 days prior to arrival : 50% charge</li><li>Cancellation within 14 days or Early Departure / No Show : 100% charge</li></ul>', NULL, '2022-10-26 08:28:36', '2023-06-27 10:53:50'),
(5, 'Amarterra Villas Bali', 'PBMDDwhKa4xXTxEDNxYmwJIZAL', 'Nusa Dua', 'Resort Lot Block B, Benoa, Kec. Kuta Sel., Kabupaten Badung, Bali 80363', 'Jose Calvin Saputra', '0361776400', '<p>Amarterra Villas Bali Nusa Dua &ndash; a part of the MGallery Hotel Collection consist of 39 luxury private pool villas located within the heart of Nusa Dua, close to the beach and offering&nbsp;an&nbsp;unparalleled five star boutique experience. Elegantly crafted with richly-textured materials, the villas&rsquo; d&eacute;cor is accentuated by intricate furnishings and fitted with 21<sup>st</sup>&nbsp;century technology for modern day living. Amarterra is the perfect oasis for honeymooners, couples, and those wanting to escape the hustle and bustle of everyday life.</p>', '<p>- Private swimming pool in each villa<br />- Whirlpool Bathtub with Jacuzzi<br />- Outdoor and indoor shower<br />- Air conditioning in all guest bedrooms<br />- Living Room with Hospitality TV<br />- HDMI &amp; converter cables available upon request<br />- IDD Telephone, Free wifi and Cable TV in all bedrooms<br />- Safety deposit boxes in each bedrooms<br />- Gymnasium &amp; Spa (under maintenance)<br />- Hotel Pool with sundeck</p>', '<p><b>Standard benefit :</b></p><p>Daily breakfast</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 'Draft', '1679976015_amarterra_villa_bali.jpg', 2, 'https://amarterravilla.com/', 'https://goo.gl/maps/czckeDJMaedjtDH56', NULL, NULL, '<p><b><u>Normal Season</u></b></p><p>Cancellations received inside 72 hours of arrival, will charge equivalent to 50% of the contracted rate for the entire stay.</p><p>Cancellations received inside 24 hours of arrival, will charge equivalent to 100% of the contracted rate for the entire stay. For reservations amendments, which shorten the stay, the same cancellation conditions will apply.</p><p><b><u>High &amp; Peak Season </u></b></p><p>Cancellations received inside 7 days of arrival, will charge equivalent to 50% of the contracted rate for the entire stay.</p><p>Cancellations received inside 5 days of arrival, will charge equivalent to 100% of the contracted rate for the entire stay. For reservations amendments which shorten the stay, the same cancellation conditions will apply</p><p><b><u>No Show</u></b></p><p>In case of a no show where the guest does not arrive, the hotel will apply a charge equivalent to 100% of the entire stay.</p>', NULL, '2022-10-26 10:38:34', '2023-03-27 17:08:29'),
(6, 'Alila Villas Uluwatu', 'pwdaAR3PKvShVefAJRvKyWXeN8', 'Uluwatu', 'Jl. Belimbing Sari Tambiyak, Pecatu, South Kuta, Badung Regency, Bali 80364', 'Miu Miu Chang', '03618482166', '<p>Set atop dramatic cliffs overlooking the Indian Ocean, in a setting that feels as if you&rsquo;re at the edge of the world, is Alila Villas Uluwatu. Here, you&rsquo;ll find a profound connection to place and self in ways unknown.</p>', '<ul><li>Wi-Fi internet access throughout the resort</li><li>Morning Yoga classes everyday from 7.30am - 8.30am</li><li>Host (butler) service</li><li>Use of 24-hour gym</li><li>Bicycles available for guests&#39; use at the resort</li><li>Alila Living bath amenities</li></ul>', '<p><b>Standard Benefit :</b></p><p>Daily breakfast</p><p><b>Children Policy :</b></p><p>Accommodation is free of charge for children between 1 - 12 years of age (to a maximum of 1 child or 1 infant per room) sharing the same room with parents and using existing bedding. A child below 6 years of age dines for free, when accompanied by paying adults. 50% discount on all contracted meal will apply for children between 6 - 12 years of age. Should additional bedding be required extra bed rate will apply.</p><p><b>Honeymoon Benefit :</b></p><p>Romantic drawn bath and scented candles, a special selection of Alila room amenities placed in the villa prior to arrival.</p><p><b>Seasonal Policy :</b></p><ul><li>Minimum 2 nights stay for Normal and High seasons and minimum 3 nights stay for Peak Season.</li><li>No check &ndash; out on 31 December, no set dinner is available on 24, 25 &amp; 31 December &amp; 1 January.</li></ul>', 'Active', '1679976107_Alila-Villas-Uluwatu-in-Bali-Sunset-Cabana.jpg', 14, 'https://www.alilahotels.com/uluwatu', 'https://g.page/alilavillasuluwatu?share', NULL, NULL, '<p><b>Normal Season </b>(01 April &ndash; 31 July, 01 Sep &ndash; 23 Dec, 06 Jan &ndash; 31 March 2024) :</p><ul><li>Cancellation less than 3 days prior to arrival : 1 night charge</li><li>No show : 1 night charge</li></ul><p><b>High Season </b>(01 &ndash; 31 Aug 2023) :</p><ul><li>Cancellation less than 14 days prior to arrival : 1 night charge</li><li>No show : 50% of the total room nights will be charged</li></ul><p><b>Peak Season </b>(24 Dec 2023 &ndash; 05 Jan 2024) :</p><ul><li>Cancellation less than 30 days prior to arrival : 100% of the total night per room reserved will be charged</li><li>No show : 100% of the total room nights will be charged</li></ul>', NULL, '2022-10-26 12:23:21', '2023-06-27 11:01:24'),
(9, 'The Anvaya Beach Resort Bali', 'mKsQuepwqJPBI0cYqwer2rEnEZ', 'Kuta', 'Jl. Kartika Plaza, Tuban, Kec. Kuta, Kabupaten Badung, Bali 80361', 'Windiya Riani', '03612090477', '<p>A hidden sanctuary in southern Bali has been reborn as the brand new The ANVAYA Beach Resort. ANVAYA derives from Sanskrit language and means connection. Drawing from this, we focus on building strong connections with our guests by providing not just an experience but also the luxury of providing you with a home away from home.</p>', '<ul><li>Free Internet Access&nbsp;</li><li>Free Parking &ndash; Restaurant</li><li>Fitness Center</li><li>Pool</li><li>Spa</li><li>Digital Key</li><li>Digital Check-In</li><li>Resort Property</li><li>Laundry</li><li>Concierge</li><li>Meeting Facilitie</li></ul>', '<p><strong>Standar Benefit :&nbsp;</strong></p><p>Daily breakfast</p><p><strong>Seasonal Policy :&nbsp;</strong></p><ul><li>Arrivals in between 23 Dec - 05 Jan each year require a minimum of 4 nights.</li><li>No Check out on 31 December.</li></ul>', 'Active', '1679976343_The Anvaya Beach Resort Bali.jpg', 14, 'https://www.theanvayabali.com/', 'https://g.page/TheANVAYABali?share', NULL, NULL, '<p><strong>Normal Season</strong> (01 April &ndash; 30 June 2023, 01 Sep &ndash; 22 Dec 2023, 06 Jan &ndash; 31 March&#39;2024) :&nbsp;</p><ul><li>Cancellation&nbsp;7 &ndash; 14 days : 1 night charge&nbsp;</li><li>Cancellation less than 7 days, no show &amp; early departure &amp; amendments : 100% of Full Stay</li></ul><p><b>High / Peak Season</b> (01 July &ndash; 31 Aug 2023, 23 Dec 2023 &ndash; 05 Jan 2024) :</p><ul><li>Cancellation 14 &ndash; 21 days : 1 night&nbsp;charge&nbsp;</li><li>Cancellation less than 14 days, no show &amp; early departure &amp; amendments : 100% of Full Stay</li></ul>', NULL, '2022-10-29 10:44:28', '2023-06-28 02:43:13'),
(10, 'Anantara Uluwatu', 'WRWwZ0VlLk9QFJVy1gnxtZ0iU8', 'Uluwatu', 'Jl. Pemutih, Jl. Labuansait, Pecatu, Kec. Kuta Sel., Kabupaten Badung, Bali 80361', 'Trisna', '03618957555', '<p>Discover a slower pace of life on the southern tip of Bali. Away from the crowds, explore clifftop temples, hidden beaches, and some of the world&rsquo;s best surf breaks. Anantara Uluwatu Bali Resort unfolds on a dramatic cliffside over the Indian Ocean. Terraced architecture ensures ocean views from every angle. Dine, swim and Jacuzzi against a panorama of sunset at our Bali resort&rsquo;s luxurious Suites. Ride the waves of the famous Impossible Beach below.</p>', '<ul><li>Mini Theatre</li><li>Surfing</li><li>Temple</li><li>Infinity Pool</li><li>Sailing</li><li>Free Internet Access</li><li>Free Parking</li><li>Restaurant</li><li>Fitness Center</li><li>Pool</li><li>Spa</li><li>Digital Key</li><li>Digital Check-In</li><li>Resort Property</li><li>Laundry</li><li>Concierge</li><li>Meeting Facilities</li></ul>', '<p><strong>Standard Benefit :</strong></p><p>Daily breakfast</p><p><strong>Anantara Uluwatu 10th years anniversary special gift :&nbsp;</strong></p><ul><li>Staying from 06 January&nbsp;&ndash; 31 Dec 2023</li><li>Free private return airport transfer for minimum stay 10 nights&nbsp;</li><li>Get discount for signature romantic dinner, signature cooking class&nbsp;</li></ul>', 'Active', '1679976465_Screenshot_2.jpg', 14, 'https://www.anantara.com/en/uluwatu-bali', 'https://goo.gl/maps/iBPshGsAWiYXAiTX7', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-10-29 11:53:03', '2023-06-28 04:49:58'),
(11, 'Alila Manggis', 'pfzsdDaw4ycZ1aLm4tlQE7JU1O', 'Karangasem', 'Desa Buitan, Manggis, Karangasem Regency, Bali 80871', 'Miu Miu Chang', '036136341011', '<p>Alila Manggis is situated within the regency of Karangasem, close to the town of Candidasa. Here the local people follow a traditional lifestyle, whether cultivating rice, farming, fishing, weaving baskets and the famous double ikat textiles, or salt making. Various walking tours are available, taking in sights like Mount Agung, home to Bali&rsquo;s mother temple at Besakih, and the spectacular terraced hillsides. Other tours can be arranged to see the traditional Bali Aga village of Tenganan, the water palaces of Tirta Gangga and Ujung, the weaving village of Sidemen, the Kerta Gosa Palace of Justice at Klungkung, and various Balinese temples. The waters east of Manggis teem with diverse marine life and are home to seven wondrous dive sites.</p>', '<ul><li>Spa Alila</li><li>Weddings</li><li>Meetings</li><li>Surya-yoga-retreat-wellness-program</li><li>Balinese Cooking Class</li><li>East Bali Trekking</li><li>Chasing Sunrise or Sunset</li></ul>', '<p><b>Standard benefit :</b></p><ul><li>Daily breakfast</li><li>Daily poolside afternoon tea</li><li>Dive instructions class every Monday from 04.00 PM - .5.00 PM</li></ul><p><b>Children policy :</b></p><p>Accommodation is free of charge for children between 1 - 11 years of age (to a maximum of 1 child or 1 infant per room) sharing the same room with parents and using existing bedding.&nbsp;</p><p><b>Honeymoon benefit :</b></p><ul><li>Daily fresh seasonal fruits, flower arrangement and scented candles.</li><li>With a minimum 3-night stay, receive &#39;sweet temptation&#39; beverages placed in the room upon arrival</li></ul><p><b>Seasonal policy :</b></p><ul><li>Minimum 2 nights stay for Normal and High seasons and minimum 3 nights stay for Peak Season.</li><li>There is no compulsory meals, check in and check out restriction during Peak Season (24 December 2023 &ndash; 5 January 2024).</li></ul>', 'Active', '1667459497_2b8ea1e633babc2d6659aba99f038fc6_XL.jpg', 14, 'https://www.alilahotels.com/manggis', 'https://goo.gl/maps/J1ui5kF9oMnPeU6i9', NULL, NULL, '<p><b>Normal Season </b>(01 April &ndash; 15 July 2023, 16 Sep &ndash; 23 Dec 2023, 06 Jan &ndash; 31 March 2024) :</p><ul><li>Cancellation less than 3 days prior to arrival : 1 night charge</li><li>No show : 1 night charge</li></ul><p><b>High Season </b>(16 July &ndash; 15 Sep 2023) :</p><ul><li>Cancellation less than 30 days prior to arrival : 1 night charge</li><li>No show : 50% of the total room nights will be charged</li></ul><p><b>Peak Season </b>(24 Dec 2023 &ndash; 05 Jan 2024)</p><ul><li>Cancellation less than 21 days prior to arrival : 100% of the total night per room reserved will be charged</li><li>No show : 100% of the total room nights will be charged</li></ul>', NULL, '2022-11-01 20:11:37', '2023-06-28 05:17:50'),
(12, 'Alila Seminyak', '09mEA3seXZJ5HhAcPGZ2lB3k5g', 'Seminyak', 'Jl. Taman Ganesha No.9 Petitenget, Seminyak, Kerobokan Kelod, Kec. Kuta Utara, Kabupaten Badung, Bali 80361', 'Hitomi Minakawa', '03613021888', '<p>Situated at the quieter end of an eight-kilometre beach that stretches north from Kuta and Legian, Seminyak has evolved into one of Bali&rsquo;s hippest scenes. There are plenty of things to do in Bali Seminyak, for instance the sea here is great for surfing, the sunsets are legendary, the beaches are some of the best in all of Bali, and the streets pulse to the beat of fashionable shopping, a world-class dining scene and notable nightlife.</p><p>Seminyak is also a great base for exploring Bali&rsquo;s hotspots, lush landscapes and cultural gems, from Uluwatu Temple in the south and Tanah Lot Temple to the north, to the beautiful rice terraces that stretch as far as the eye can see. Everything you could want in one perfect Balinese getaway.</p>', '<ul><li>Spa Alila</li><li>Kombucha Pairing Afternoon Tea</li><li>Junior Happenings</li><li>Mineral Ritual</li><li>Alila-happenings</li><li>beach-bar</li></ul>', '<p><b>Standard benefit :</b></p><p>Daily breakfast</p><p><b>Children policy :</b></p><p>Accommodation is free of charge for children between 1 - 11 years of age (to a maximum of 1 child or 1 infant per room) sharing the same room with parents and using existing bedding. A child below 4 years of age dines for free, when accompanied by paying adults. 50% discount on all contracted meal will apply for children between 4 - 11 years of age. Should additional bedding be required extra bed rate will apply.</p><p><b>Honeymoon benefit :</b></p><p>Seasonal fresh fruits and a celebration cake placed in the room upon arrival</p><p><b>Seasonal policy :</b></p><ul><li>Minimum 2 nights stay for Normal and High seasons and minimum 3 nights stay for Peak Season.</li><li>No set dinner inclusion is available in 24, 25 &amp; 31 December &amp; 1 January.</li></ul>', 'Active', '1667461044_Alila+Seminyak+-+Panorama.jpg', 14, 'https://www.alilahotels.com/seminyak', 'https://g.page/alilaseminyak?share', NULL, NULL, '<p><b>Normal Season </b>(6 Jan &ndash; 31 July 2023, 1 Sep &ndash; 23 Dec 2023) :</p><ul><li>Cancellation less than 3 days prior to arrival : 1 night charge</li><li>No show : 1 night charge</li></ul><p><b>High Season </b>(1 &ndash; 31 Aug 2023) :</p><ul><li>Cancellation less than 14 days prior to arrival : 1 night charge</li><li>No show : 50% of the total room nights will be charged</li></ul><p><b>Peak Season </b>(24 Dec 2023 &ndash; 05 Jan 2024) :</p><ul><li>Cancellation less than 45 days prior to arrival : 100% of the total night per room reserved will be charged</li><li>No show : 100% of the total room nights will be charged</li></ul>', NULL, '2022-11-01 20:37:24', '2023-06-28 09:25:00'),
(13, 'Alila Ubud', 'Jvjb4FyAZRWu8kyGx2kM1MssnS', 'Ubud', 'Desa, Melinggih Kelod, Payangan, Gianyar Regency, Bali 80572', 'Miu Miu Chang', '0361975963', '<p>For over a century, since becoming a Dutch protectorate in 1900 at its own request, Ubud has been a centre for traditional arts and culture. In the 1930s, when foreign artists were encouraged by the royal family to take up residence in the town, Ubud became a base for the likes of Walter Spies and Rudolph Bonnet, who were instrumental in promoting an understanding of Balinese art and cultural heritage worldwide. From the 1960s onwards, intrepid travellers began to arrive in earnest, drawn by its hive of creative energy. Since then, Ubud has developed into a world-class international destination while maintaining its integrity as the centre of Balinese arts and culture. Stay at our luxurious Ubud villa resort and experience the very best this enchanting island has to offer.</p>', '<ul><li>Spa Alila</li><li>VW Retro Safari Tour</li><li>Rainforest-retreat</li><li>Spice-market</li><li>Unesco-experience</li><li>Wedding</li><li>Meeting</li></ul>', '<p><b>Standard Benefit :</b></p><ul><li>Daily breakfast</li><li>Daily poolside afternoon tea</li></ul><p><b>Children Policy :</b></p><p>Accommodation is free of charge for children between 1 - 11 years of age (to a maximum of 1 child or 1 infant per room) sharing the same room with parents and using existing bedding. A child below 4 years of age dines for free, when accompanied by paying adults. 50% discount on all contracted meal will apply for children between 4 - 11 years of age. Should additional bedding be required extra bed rate will apply.</p><p><b>Honeymoon Benefit :</b></p><p>Balinese flower arrangement and an exclusive couple celebration amenities consist of champagne (fruits champagne for non-alcoholic) on arrival, fruits baskets, sweet tooth amenity, and romantic turndown set up on the first night.</p><p><b>Seasonal Policy :</b></p><ul><li>Minimum 2 nights stay for Normal and High seasons and minimum 3 nights stay for Peak Season.</li><li>No check out on 31 December and 1 January</li><li>No set dinner inclusion is available in 24, 25 &amp; 31 December &amp; 1 January.</li></ul>', 'Active', '1667461511_Alila-Ubud-Aerial-07.jpg', 14, 'https://www.alilahotels.com/ubud', 'https://goo.gl/maps/6jm1sGMDtBvEi8Jt7', NULL, NULL, '<p><b>Normal Season</b>&nbsp;(01 April &ndash; 15 July 2023, 16 Sep &ndash; 23 Dec 2023, 06 Jan &ndash; 31 March 2024) :</p><ul><li>Cancellation less than 3 days prior to arrival : 1 night charge</li><li>No show : 1 night charge</li></ul><p><b>High Season</b>&nbsp;(16 July &ndash; 15 Sep 2023) :</p><ul><li>Cancellation less than 30 days prior to arrival : 1 night charge</li><li>No show : 50% of the total room nights will be charged</li></ul><p><b>Peak Season </b>(24 Dec 2023 &ndash; 05 Jan 2024) :&nbsp;</p><ul><li>Cancellation less than 21 days prior to arrival : 100% of the total night per room reserved will be charged</li><li>No show : 100% of the total room nights will be charged</li></ul><p><b>No Show :&nbsp;</b></p><ul><li>In case of a no show where the guest does not arrive, the hotel will apply a charge equivalent to 100% of the entire stay.</li></ul>', NULL, '2022-11-01 20:45:11', '2023-06-30 05:11:04'),
(14, 'Amankila', 'VhoI6MtSuxBCMKWCVqnLQj0CAA', 'Karangasem', 'Jl. Raya Manggis, Manggis, Kec. Manggis, Kabupaten Karangasem, 80871 ,Bali, Indonesia', 'Anna Nash', '036341333', '<p>Claiming a breathtaking stretch of coastline on the Lombok Strait, Amankila rests on a lush hillside beneath sacred Mount Agung. Connected by frangipani-lined walkways through the treetops, stilted suites offer spectacular views high on the hillside, while a three-tier infinity pool cascades at the property&rsquo;s heart and the Beach Club leads to a private black-sand beach.&nbsp;</p>', '<p>- aman-bali-break<br />- Wellness &amp; Fitness at Amankila<br />- Tamansari Hill<br />- amankila-romance</p>', '<p>* Inclusion : Daily Breakfast , Return Airport Transfer</p>', 'Active', '1667462109_20060o000000ff3ti172B_Z_1100_824_R5_Q70_D.webp', 2, 'https://www.aman.com/resorts/amankila', 'https://goo.gl/maps/FevPiwpDbzGF5qNT9', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-11-01 20:55:09', '2023-03-27 20:09:59'),
(15, 'Ametis Villa Canggu', 'OblGAYHFnhfLUgz41W2DrLQy8O', 'Canggu', 'Jl. Pantai Batu Bolong No.99, Canggu, Kec. Kuta Utara, Kabupaten Badung, 80361	,Bali, Indonesia', 'Akiko Yoshioka', '03618445557', '<p>While the passage of time has wrought certain changes, the true essence of Bali remains the same and Ametis Villa is the place for you experience the very soul of this heavenly island.</p><p>Located in Canggu, Ametis Villa is about 35 minutes from Kuta. This area maintains its cultural roots and is dotted with productive rice terraces that extend to a rugged stretch of coastline. Canggu is popular within surfing and expatriate circles, sought out for its laidback lifestyle qualities away from the crowds and concrete jungle of Seminyak.</p><p>Ametis Villa is a luxury lifestyle villa with a home-style concept that will make you feel like you truly belong. During your stay, you will be assigned a personal butler, who excels in the singular ability to anticipate your every need, and to exceed your every expectation.</p><p>Conceived, built and managed with integrity, Ametis Villa is respectful of Bali&#39;s unique cultural heritage, seeks to interact with the local community and shows sensitivity towards the immediate environment</p>', '<p>- Cruising/Sailing/Scuba Diving/Snorkelling<br />- Surfing<br />- White Water Rafting<br />- Golf and Tennis<br />- Fishing<br />- Horse Riding<br />- Elephant Safari Park<br />- Water Sports<br />- Surfing and Body Boarding<br />- Waterbom Park<br />- Bali Bird Park Safari<br />- Bali Safari &amp; Marine Park<br />- RUBY SPA<br />- Private Villa</p>', '<p><b>Standard benefit :</b></p><p>Daily breakfast, Personal butler service, personalized villa check in&amp;out, 30Mins relaxing massage, daily sunset cocktail and canapes 18.00-20.00, daily afternoon tea 15.00-18.00, daily restocked minibar (soft drink, beer), daily restocked coffee, ea and homemade snack in villa, daily replenished fresh fruit in villa</p><p>Add value for stay in Imperial Villa : upgrade 1x30mins into 60mins body massage at Ruby Spa, daily laundry up to 8 pieces/day/villa</p><p><b>Children policy :</b></p><p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Accommodation at Ametis Villa is available only for guest aged 12 years and above</p><p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Children aged between 12 years and 16 years old have alternative to stay with their parents in the same villa on existing sofa bed in Imperial Villa and Grand Villa</p><p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Eternal home-style dining and Ametis Lounge is available for children under 12 years old who should be accompanied by parents or guardian.</p><p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; In case Ametis Villa receives guest check-in with children under 12 years old without any advance notice, Ametis Villa has full authority to relocate guest to another hotel.</p><p><b>Honeymoon benefit :</b></p><p>&bull; Honeymoon flower and cake upon arrival</p><p>&bull; Departure gift</p><p><b>Seasonal policy :</b></p><p>No Check-in nor Check-out is allowed on 31st December 2022</p>', 'Draft', '1667463022_234148112.jpg', 2, 'https://www.ametisvilla.com/', 'https://g.page/ametisvillabali?share', NULL, NULL, '<p><b>Regular Season:</b></p><p>&bull; 14 days before arrival: one night cancellation fee per villa</p><p>&bull; 7 days before arrival: full night&rsquo;s cancellation fee per villa</p><p>&bull; No shows and early departures will be charged in full for the total number of nights per room reserved</p><p><b>High Season:</b></p><p>&bull; 21 days before arrival: one night cancellation fee per villa</p><p>&bull; 14 days before arrival: full night&rsquo;s cancellation fee per villa</p><p>&bull; No shows and early departures will be charged in full for the total number of nights per room reserved</p><p><b>Peak Season:</b></p><p>&bull; 30 days before arrival: one night cancellation fee per villa</p><p>&bull; 21 days before arrival: full night&rsquo;s cancellation fee per villa</p><p>&bull; No shows and early departures will be charged in full for the total number of nights per room reserved</p>', NULL, '2022-11-01 21:10:22', '2023-04-17 19:22:08'),
(16, 'Andaz Bali', 'PERXJY3kqZptq5hrmGJK0FuNvL', 'Sanur', 'Jl. Danau Tamblingan No.89A, Sanur, Denpasar Selatan, Kota Denpasar	,Bali, Indonesia', 'Ketut Sumerta', '03613201234', '<p>Modeled after a modern Balinese village, the resort invites guests to discover the fascinating old and new. The beachfront resort is carefully built around existing mature landscape, lending it a homey and lush ambience, much like Sanur itself.</p>', '<p>- Free Internet Access<br />- Free Parking<br />- On-Site Restaurant<br />- Fitness Center<br />- Pool<br />- Spa<br />- Digital Key<br />- Digital Check-In<br />- Camp Hyatt<br />- Resort Property<br />- Laundry<br />- Concierge<br />- Meeting Facilities</p>', '<p><b>Standard benefit :</b></p><p>Daily breakfast</p><p><b>Children policy :</b></p><p>Children 6 years old and under is free stay with sharing bed with parents</p><p><b>Seasonal policy :</b></p><p>Minimum 2 consecutive nights stay required for all season.</p><p>Minimum 3 consecutive nights stay required during New Year Eve&rsquo;s period (23 Dec &ndash; 04 Jan).</p>', 'Active', '1667463682_DPSAZ-P0451-Santhi-Exterior.16x9.webp', 2, 'https://www.hyatt.com/en-US/hotel/indonesia/andaz-bali/', 'https://g.page/andazbali?share', NULL, NULL, '<p>Normal season : 72 hours prior to arrival or no show: One (01) night room charge will be applied<br />High / Peak season : 14 days prior to arrival or no show: One (01) night room charge will be applied.</p>', NULL, '2022-11-01 21:21:22', '2023-03-28 19:05:10'),
(17, 'Ayana Resort And Spa', 'KICqjCZMn5sW6gCi8BrRtfhBJn', 'Jimbaran', 'Jl. Karang Mas Sejahtera Jimbaran 80364', 'Noriko Takano', '0361702222', '<p>With full access to all dining and recreation at both AYANA and RIMBA and a complimentary resort shuttle, guests enjoy the most extensive on-site facilities of any resort in Bali. There are 19 restaurants and bars including the famous Rock Bar; secluded white sand beach; 12 swimming pools; world-class Spa with Hydrotherapy Seawater Pool and Spa on the Rocks treatment; golf-putting and fitness center; and complimentary WiFi.</p><p>Located at RIMBA, the sister property, and surrounded by a stunning lake, rice paddy, and edible gardens; Kampoeng Bali is a stand-alone restaurant with an outdoor amphitheater that welcomes you into an authentic Balinese village experience. Enjoy an extensive Balinese buffet with live cooking stations as well as an exciting Kecak performance beneath the stars.</p>', '<p>- Golf Putting Course<br />- Ayana Kids Club<br />- Spa<br />- Jogging Trail<br />- Rimba Kids Club<br />- Rimba Gym<br />-Ayana GYM</p>', '<p>* Daily Breakfast | Benefit : Additional 1x1hour Aquatonic Pool at Ayana Spa and Rock BarSunset Time 1glass of Beer or Soft Drink</p>', 'Active', '1667464646_gallery_experience__unique_pool.jpg', 14, 'https://www.ayana.com/bali/', 'https://goo.gl/maps/if722YzNKMBHSkUT9', NULL, NULL, '<p><strong>Regular Season</strong></p><p>Cancellation 7 days prior to arrival 1 night charge&nbsp;</p><p><strong>High Season&nbsp;</strong></p><p>Cancellation 14 days prior to arrival 1 night charge&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Peak Season&nbsp;</strong></p><p>Cancellation 30 days prior to arrival full charge&nbsp;</p><p><strong>No Show&nbsp;</strong></p><p>* A reservation is considered &ldquo;no show&rdquo; if arrival does not occur on the date reserved and the Hotel is not notified of any emergency delays in writing. No show will be subject to a penalty equal to &ldquo;a full charge on whole period of stay&rdquo; (including all the additional arrangement).</p><p>* No show must be paid without reliance on billed vouchers since the clients did not arrive in the hotel, no voucher will be submitted.&nbsp;</p>', NULL, '2022-11-01 21:37:26', '2023-05-29 07:06:28'),
(18, 'Jumeirah Bali', 'eJnIvMbtJi6PGwKNp33itM9hen', 'Pecatu', 'Pecatu Indah Resort, Jl. Raya Uluwatu Street, South Kuta, Badung Regency	,Bali, Indonesia', 'Octaviany Mona Kalalo', '03612015000', '<p>An elegant haven inspired by a tranquil Javanese-Hindu water palace</p>', '<p>- Luxury Airport Transfers<br />- Personal Butler Service<br />- Peafowl Pavilion Kids Club<br />- Holistic Wellness Experiences<br />- Beach Boot Camp<br />- Blessings of Bali<br />- Sunrise to Sunset Meditation<br />&nbsp;</p>', '<p><b>Standard benefit :</b></p><p>Daily breakfast</p><p><b>Children policy :</b></p><p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Child 0-3 years old all meals free of charge in the all-day dining restaurant</p><p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Baby cot at no extra charge and subject to availability</p><p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Child 4-12 years old breakfast supplement 50% charge from adult breakfast rate</p><p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Children&rsquo;s menu is available in all casual dining restaurant</p><p><b>Seasonal policy :</b></p><p>No Check-in or Check-out is allowed on 31st December</p>', 'Active', '1667465380_jcom_hero_imagejumeirah-bali--resort-ocean-view__landscape.jpg', 2, 'https://www.jumeirah.com/en', 'https://g.page/jumeirahbali?share', NULL, NULL, '<p>New Year Period &ndash; Arrivals from 27th to 31st December: minimum length of stay 3 nights.<br />No check-in or check-out is permitted on 31st December.<br />No check-in or check-out is permitted on 11 March 2014 (Silent Day).</p><p><b><u>Normal Season</u></b></p><p>Cancellation within 14 days or less prior to arrival at 15:00 hours, 100% charge on total booking</p><p><b><u>High Season </u></b></p><p>Cancellation within 21 days or less prior to arrival at 15:00 hours, 100% charge on total booking</p><p><b><u>Peak Season</u></b></p><p>Cancellation within 45 days or less prior to arrival at 15:00 hours, 100% charge on total booking</p><p><b><u>No Show</u></b></p><p>In case of a no show where the guest does not arrive, the hotel will apply a charge equivalent to 100% of the entire stay.</p>', NULL, '2022-11-01 21:49:40', '2023-03-28 19:58:56'),
(19, 'Sheraton Bali Kuta Resort', '0iEsCUInXr9R44V3Ll1GBSNp0P', 'Kuta', 'Jl. Pantai Kuta, Kuta, Kec. Kuta, Kabupaten Badung, Bali 80361', 'Novitasari', '03618465555', '<p>Immerse yourself in a beach lover&#39;s paradise at Sheraton Bali Kuta Resort. Located in downtown Kuta, Bali, our hotel adjoins the Beachwalk mall with 200 luxury shops and a cineplex. Stroll to Kuta Beach where the sandy shore is lined with coconut trees. Indulge in a body treatment at Shine Spa for Sheraton&trade;. Take a dip in our outdoor infinity pool. Stay connected here in Kuta, with computer workstations in our lobby. Maintain your gym routine at Sheraton Fitness&reg;. Choose Italian cuisine with local twist at Bene Italian Kitchen or sip cocktails or afternoon tea with ocean views in The Lounge. Select from among 203 hotel rooms or suites featuring our Sheraton Signature Sleep Experience. All rooms offer private balconies - many with Indian Ocean views. Explore Kuta, Bali, with ease from our resort. The beach, the ocean, the treasures of Bali and our signature service await you at our 5-star Kuta resort</p>', '<p>- Free Internet Access<br />- Free Parking<br />- Restaurant<br />- Fitness Center<br />- Pool<br />- Spa<br />- Digital Key<br />- Digital Check-In<br />- Resort Property<br />- Laundry<br />- Concierge<br />- Meeting Facilities&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>', '<p><b>Standard benefit :</b></p><p>Daily breakfast</p><p><b>Children policy :</b></p><p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; No Additional charge for children under 12 years of age sharing room with parents without extra bed, additional breakfast will be charged</p><p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Children below 3 years old will be provided complimentary buffet meals at available restaurant when accompanying an adult who is having a full paying meal.</p><p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Children from 3 to 11.99 years old will be charged 50% of meals in all venues except children&rsquo;s menu</p><p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Baby cot is complimentary.</p><p><b>Honeymoon/Anniversary benefit :</b></p><p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Flower arrangement.</p><p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Rose petals on the bed and bathtub.</p><p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Complimentary honeymoon cake.</p><p><b>Seasonal policy :</b></p><p>Minimum stay of two (2) nights applies for stay thru 30 December 2023 &ndash; 01 January 202</p>', 'Active', '1667785694_2420702_v3.webp', 5, 'https://www.sheratonbalikuta.co.id/', 'https://g.page/sheratonkuta?share', NULL, NULL, '<p><b><u>Normal Season</u></b></p><p>Cancellation within 7 days of arrival : 1 night penalty charged</p><p>Cancellation within 3 days of arrival : 100% penalty charged</p><p><b><u>High Season </u></b></p><p>Cancellation within 14 days of arrival : 1 night penalty charged</p><p>Cancellation within 7 days of arrival : 100% penalty charged</p><p><b><u>Peak Season</u></b></p><p>Cancellation within 30 days of arrival : 1 night penalty charged</p><p>Cancellation within 14 days of arrival : 100% penalty charged</p><p><b><u>No Show</u></b></p><p>In case of a no show where the guest does not arrive, the hotel will apply a charge equivalent to 100% of the entire stay.</p>', NULL, '2022-11-05 14:48:14', '2023-02-05 05:42:54'),
(20, 'Bvlgari Resort', 'GKPKEF6FDEpkTfVIcBNhQhR7jI', 'Uluwatu', 'Banjar Dinas Kangin Jalan Goa Lempeh Jalan Raya Uluwatu, Kabupaten Badung, Bali 80364', 'Putu Sulistiawati', '03618471000', '<p>The Bulgari Resort Bali is located in one of the most exclusive destinations in the world, a veritable emblem of the tropical exoticism of the Orient, combining the breathtaking beauty of unspoiled nature of Bali beach resorts with a sophisticated contemporary design born from the encounter between traditional Balinese forms and high Italian style. The quality of the services along with the views of the Indian Ocean offered by its magnificent position 150 meters over the sea are the perfect introduction to the second luxury hotels from Bulgari Hotels &amp; Resorts.</p>', '<p>Villa and Spa</p>', '<p>Daily breakfast</p>', 'Draft', '1668395757_Bulgari Lobby.jpg', 5, 'https://www.bulgarihotels.com/en_US/bali', 'https://goo.gl/maps/vZqwp21Z48YLstxp9', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-11-12 16:15:57', '2022-11-30 14:37:42'),
(21, 'Padma Legian', 'xdobOFg5SOZkV9BVhq01o8S0Vb', 'Kuta', 'Jl. Padma No. 1 Legian - Bali 80361 Indonesia', 'Yuliaty Lawandra', '0361752111', '<p>Situated in 6.8 hectares of beautifully manicured gardens filled with lush tropical greenery, water features, swimming pools and stunning public art, Padma Resort Legian is a warm and welcoming luxury five-star resort immersed in the rich heritage, arts and culture of Bali.</p><p>With a prime beachfront location in the heart of Legian, an area renowned for its beautiful sunsets, entertainment, night life, restaurants and boutique shopping, Padma Resort Legian offers a choice of stylish contemporary and Balinese-inspired accommodation backed by world-class facilities, event spaces and the celebrated Balinese hospitality and charm.</p>', '<p>- Swimming Pool</p><p>- Fitness Center</p><p>- Spa</p><p>- Tennis Court</p><p>- Kids Club</p><p>- Shop</p><p>- Guest Services</p><p>- Transportation</p>', '<p><b>Standard benefit :</b></p><p>Daily breakfast</p><p><b>Children policy :</b></p><p>No Additional charge for children age 0 - 5 years of age stay with parents</p><p><b>Honeymoon/Anniversary benefit :</b></p><p>Flower and fruits upon arrival and 1x Honeymoon cake (advance booking is required)</p><p><b>Seasonal policy :</b></p><p>No check out on 31 December 2023</p><p>No check in &ndash; check out on Nyepi Day of 2024</p><p>No compulsory dinner on Christmas Eve and New Year</p>', 'Active', '1668400058_Padma Legian.jpg', 2, 'https://padmaresortlegian.com/', 'https://www.google.com/maps/search/padma+legian/@-8.7041474,115.1651316,17z/data=!3m1!4b1', NULL, NULL, '<p><b><u>Normal Season</u></b></p><p>Cancellation within 7 days of arrival : 1 night penalty charged</p><p><b><u>High Season </u></b></p><p>Cancellation within 14 days of arrival : 1 night penalty charged</p><p><b><u>Peak Season</u></b></p><p>Cancellation within 21 days of arrival : 1 night penalty charged</p><p><b><u>No Show</u></b></p><p>In case of a no show where the guest does not arrive, the hotel will apply a charge equivalent to 100% of the entire stay.</p>', NULL, '2022-11-12 17:27:38', '2023-04-17 19:37:06'),
(22, 'Villa Jerami', 'Lx8wprWbvicj94kpktkXHriudL', 'Kuta', 'Jl. Bali Deli No.1, Seminyak, Kec. Kuta, Kabupaten Badung, Bali 80361', 'Ni Nyoman Sukarini', '03618475970', '<p>Villa Jerami is a luxurious private villa complex of 19 luxurious homes superbly located in the heart of Seminyak, Bali. Carefully designed to combine serene Balinese touches with a modern minimalist style, Villa Jerami is understated and elegant with a fantastic sense of privacy.<br />This tropical sanctuary offers you a unique experience while on holiday in Bali; from culinary delights from our restaurant or in your villa to total body and soul pampering in our Spa.<br />Located in one of Bali`s most sought after areas, Villa Jerami covers almost one hectare of land in the cosmopolitan neighborhood of Seminyak.<br />Close to world class boutiques, designer shops and food choices from around the world, we are wonderfully positioned to allow you to enjoy the very best of what Bali has to offer while retaining the original charm that Bali is so famous for.</p>', '<p>Private wimming pool in each villa</p>', '<p>- Daily breakfast<br />-&nbsp;Contract Rate is Valid for a minimum of 2 Nights consecutive stay during low season and a minimum of 3 Nights consecutive stay during high season<br />-&nbsp;Bookings made in Peak Season, for arrivals within 21 December &ndash; 5 January must be for a minimum of 5 nights stay with no check-in and no check-out on 31 December and 1 January</p>', 'Active', '1668486517_Villa-Jerami-Luxury-Villa-Spa.jpg', 2, 'https://www.villajerami.com/', 'https://goo.gl/maps/3NvZ9VxRLAWoiVfC6', NULL, NULL, '<p><strong>CHILDREN POLICY:</strong><br />Child 0-4 years old sharing existing bedding with parents, breakfast free of charge</p>', NULL, '2022-11-13 17:28:37', '2023-03-29 16:11:28'),
(23, 'Aloft Bali Kuta at Beachwalk', 'hyi7Bs7d6WjlJwXmqjqtPfsSAX', 'Kuta', 'Beachwalk Shopping Center, Jl. Pantai Kuta, Kuta, Kec. Kuta, Kabupaten Badung, Bali 80361', 'VICKY DWIKI', '03612014888', '<p>Kick your holiday up a notch at Aloft Bali Kuta at Beachwalk, where urban style, innovative designs and technology come together. Tucked in the bustling Kuta neighborhood just steps away from famous shores&nbsp;and iconic Poppies Lane, our new-age, four-star hotel offers easy-breezy access to Bali&rsquo;s largest shopping mall and Legian&#39;s vibrant nightlife. We&#39;re the perfect hub for savvy travelers to rejuvenate and reconnect thanks to open, vibrant spaces. Chill and mingle over signature cocktails, eclectic live music and games in our integrated lobby lounge and bar. Relax in loft-inspired Kuta hotel rooms featuring private balconies, work desks with ergonomic chairs and amenities such as keyless room access and fast, free Wi-Fi. Treat yourself to new-wave culinary delights at our all-day restaurant or sweet, savory and healthy bites from our 24/7 grab-and-go zone. Soak up the sun at our outdoor pool, break out a sweat at Re:charge gym or meet and greet in meeting spaces when you choose Aloft Bali Kuta at Beachwalk.</p>', '<p>- Sustainability<br />- Restaurant<br />-&nbsp;Outdoor Pool<br />-&nbsp;Fitness Center<br />-&nbsp;Meeting Space<br />-&nbsp;Dry Cleaning Service<br />-&nbsp;Laundry<br />-&nbsp;Wake up Calls<br />-&nbsp;Daily Housekeeping<br />-&nbsp;Service Request</p>', '<p>- Daily breakfast<br />-&nbsp;Minimum stay of two (2) nights applies for stay thru 30 December 2022 &ndash; 2 January 2023</p>', 'Active', '1668581619_Aloft Bali Kuta.jpg', 2, 'https://www.marriott.com/en-us/hotels/', 'https://goo.gl/maps/2K5fdYynLLeKQMbk9', NULL, NULL, '<p>Regular Season<br />Within 7 days of arrival 1 night penalty charged Within 3 days of arrival 100% penalty charged</p><p>High Season<br />Within 14 days of arrival 1 night penalty charged Within 7 days of arrival 100% penalty charged</p><p>Peak Season<br />Within 30 days of arrival 1 night penalty charged Within 14 days of arrival 100% penalty charged No Show Clients who do not show will be charged for the entire length of stay.</p><p>Noshows must be paid without reliance on vouchers due to the inability of the client to present the voucher. Should the Company fail to pay the cancellation fee, Hotel may cancel the Company&rsquo;s billing privileges or this letter, at Hotel&rsquo;s sole discretion, without any obligation or liability whatsoever.</p><p>Early Departure Full length of stay will be chargeable.</p>', NULL, '2022-11-14 19:53:39', '2023-01-25 04:17:42'),
(24, 'Renaissance Uluwatu', '6Q6DRtlNawkASiiVSRlLYcqYvC', 'Uluwatu', 'Jalan Pantai Balangan 1 no. 1, Ungasan, Bali, Indonesia, 80361', 'Augustina Tandun', '03612003588', '<p>At Renaissance Bali Uluwatu Resort &amp; Spa, we offer a five-star resort experience amidst the tranquility of the sand and ocean. Surrounded by pristine Bali beaches, our family-friendly Uluwatu resort inspires you to relax in hotel rooms and suites featuring floating baths, plush beds, complimentary Wi-Fi and views from your private balcony. Savor Indonesian cuisine while you take in the live music and activities at Roosterfish Beach Club. Enjoy resort-style amenities like our outdoor pools, free breakfast, 24-hour gym, valet parking and on-site restaurants and bars, including our pool bar. Visit popular Bali sites, including GWK Cultural Park, Uluwatu Temple and Bali Nusa Dua Convention Center. Balance your mind and body with massages, beauty and wellness therapies at our hotel spa. Our five-star resort overlooks miles of beaches and offers an authentic Indonesian experience in Uluwatu. Unforgettable stays in Bali begin at Renaissance Bali Uluwatu Resort &amp; Spa.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p>&bull; Restaurant<br />&bull; Fitness Center<br />&bull; Spa<br />&bull; Outdool pool<br />&bull; Meeting space<br />&bull; Room Service</p>', '<p>- Daily breakfast<br />- Extra Bed is not available in Deluxe Room categories.<br />- Minimum length of stay is three (3) nights for booking stay over 30 and 31 December.<br />- No Check out on 31st December</p><p><strong>Extra Person Policy:</strong><br />- Maximum occupancy for Deluxe, Deluxe Ocean and Deluxe Terrace Ocean for adults is two (2) people and one (1) child under 12 years old based on sharing bed.<br />- Maximum occupancy for Junior Suite and Executive Suite is three (3) adults or two (2) adults and one (1) child under 12 years old with additional rollaway bed.<br />- Extra Bed is not available in Deluxe Room categories.<br />- Twin bed room type is furnished with two (2) queen size beds (140 cm x 200 cm).<br />- 3rd person (adult or children) will be charged IDR 600,000 net per night for extra bed include breakfast (please note that due to room layout, extra bed is not recommended in deluxe rooms category)<br />-&nbsp;One child below 12 years old sharing room with parents using existing bed will be charge for breakfast only at IDR 125,000 net per night<br />-&nbsp;Children below 6 years old when sharing room with parents using existing bed will be free of charge including breakfast.</p>', 'Active', '1668658935_Renaissance Uluwatu.jpg', 2, 'https://www.marriott.com/en-us/hotels/dpsuw-renaissance-bali-uluwatu-resort-and-spa/overview/', 'https://g.page/RenaissanceUluwatu?share', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-11-15 17:22:15', '2023-03-28 14:06:54'),
(25, 'Aman Villas', 'WYQMVtoxw2jRGDw60QMkGD3HI9', 'Nusa Dua', 'Jl. Desa Sawangan Jl. Nusa Dua, Benoa, Kec. Kuta Sel., Kabupaten Badung, Bali 80363', 'Balawati Putri', '03618468585', '<p>On Bali&rsquo;s southernmost peninsula, famed for its golden beaches, ocean-side temples and frangipani-scented hillsides, Aman Villas at Nusa Dua rest poolside in lush tropical gardens. The perfect starting point for a journey through Indonesia, each is an Eden-like retreat serviced by two butlers and a private chef, providing easy access to a private Beach Club and the Bali National Golf Club.&nbsp;</p>', '<p>- Free Internet Access</p><p>- Free Parking</p><p>- Restaurant</p><p>- Fitness Center</p><p>- Pool</p><p>- Spa</p><p>- Digital Key</p><p>- Digital Check-In</p><p>- Resort Property</p><p>- Laundry</p><p>- Concierge</p><p>- Meeting Facilities</p>', '<p>Daily beakfast</p><p>Minimum 2N stay</p>', 'Active', '1668659850_Aman-Villas-at-Nusa-Dua.jpg', 2, 'https://www.aman.com/villas/aman-villas-at-nusa-dua', 'https://g.page/aman-villas-at-nusa-dua?share', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-11-15 17:37:30', '2023-03-29 17:26:12'),
(26, 'Amandari Ubud', 'FBGclJKzMYQls5kP9nbcYMS83d', 'Ubud', 'Jl. Raya Kedewatan, Kedewatan, Kecamatan Ubud, Kabupaten Gianyar, Bali 80571', 'Balawati Putri', '0361975333', '<p>Presided over by a sacred stone tiger, Amandari was designed after a traditional Balinese village on the verdant lip of the Ayung River Gorge. Free-standing guest suites are reached via winding pathways, while the curving swimming pool mimics the rice paddies below. Close to the artistic centre of Ubud, this place of peace invites both reflection and the exploration of Bali&rsquo;s cultural heart.</p>', '<p>- Free Internet Access</p><p>- Free Parking</p><p>- Restaurant</p><p>- Fitness Center</p><p>- Pool</p><p>- Spa</p><p>- Digital Key</p><p>- Digital Check-In</p><p>- Resort Property</p><p>- Laundry</p><p>- Concierge</p><p>- Meeting Facilities</p>', '<p>- Daily breakfast</p><p>- No room charge applies, brekfast include</p>', 'Active', '1682323375_210204_AmanHero_Landscape_Amandari.jpg', 2, 'https://www.aman.com/resorts/amandari', 'https://g.page/amandari-resort?share', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-11-15 17:51:56', '2023-04-24 01:02:55'),
(27, 'Courtyard by Marriott Bali Nusa Dua Resort', 'GaStu1WLOLRQd90CQsjRzp5YPf', 'Nusa Dua', 'Kawasan Pariwisata Lot Sw1, Jl. Nusa Dua, Benoa, Bali, Kabupaten Badung	,Bali, Indonesia', 'Putu Widyawati', '03613003888', '<p>Discover the relaxed comfort and exceptional service awaiting you at Courtyard Bali Nusa Dua Resort. Our award-winning hotel is a few miles from the airport via our shuttle service. Unwind in our Nusa Dua five-star resort accommodations with amenities like complimentary Wi-Fi and a flat-screen TV, a marble bathroom and a private balcony with scenic views of the resort and Nusa Dua beach. Stop by one of our inviting dining outlets to enjoy all-day cuisine, to-go snacks or poolside refreshments. There&#39;s no better way to bask in the Bali sunshine than at our resort&#39;s lagoon pool. Our youngest guests can have fun at the Kids&#39; Club or at the children&#39;s pool and lazy river. Pamper yourself with a luxury treatment at the resort spa, challenge yourself in the gym or take the complimentary shuttle to our Beach Club and spend the day relaxing on Nusa Dua Beach. Those hosting an event in Bali can explore our hotel&#39;s versatile indoor and outdoor venues as well. Plan your getaway to our Nusa Dua, Bali, resort today</p>', '<p>- Complimentary&nbsp;</p><p>- Wi-Fi</p><p>- Swimming pool Adult &amp; Kid</p><p>- Whirlpool</p><p>- Beach Club</p><p>- Gym</p><p>- Spa</p><p>- Yoga</p><p>- In Room Dining</p><p>- Meeting room</p><p>- Restaurants and bars</p>', '<p>Daily breakfast</p><p>Minimum of 4 continuous stay is required during Peak Season (23 December 2022 &ndash; 5 January 2023)</p><p>No Check Out is permitted on December 31st</p>', 'Active', '1668665477_Courtyard by Marriot.webp', 14, 'https://www.marriott.com/en-us/hotels/dpscy-courtyard-bali-nusa-dua-resort/overview/', 'https://g.page/CourtyardBali?share', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-11-15 19:11:17', '2023-06-07 08:54:03');
