(28, 'Grand Hyatt Bali', 'LwgtSVMkinI2Yx9I2N8Gdz9aW5', 'Nusa Dua', 'Kawasan Wisata Nusa Dua BTDC, Jl. Nusa Dua, Badung Regency, Bali 80363', 'Fenny Juliana', '062361771234', '<p>Like the fabled Balinese water palaces of old, Grand Hyatt Bali is a cluster of four ethnic villages set amidst an inter-linking system of cascading waterfalls, landscaped gardens and lagoons that meander through 41 acres of lush tropical gardens, located along a 650-meter beach front of Nusa Dua&#39;s pristine beach.</p>', '<p>- Free Internet Access</p><p>- Free Parking</p><p>- On-Site Restaurant</p><p>- Fitness Center</p><p>- Pool</p><p>- Spa</p><p>- Digital Key</p><p>- Digital Check-In</p><p>- Resort Property</p><p>- Laundry</p><p>- Concierge</p><p>- Meeting Facilities&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />&nbsp;</p>', '<p><b>Standard benefit :</b></p><p>Daily breakfast</p><p><b>Children policy :</b></p><p>- Children 12 years old and under, complimentary used of day bed measuring 1.3 meters x 2.0 meters at Grand Room/ Ocean view/ Grand Club Garden View Rooms</p><p>- Child under twelve (12) years old can be accommodated IF utilizing the same bed only as parents at Grand Club Deluxe Garden</p><p><b>Seasonal policy :</b></p><p>- Minimum 2 consecutive nights stay required for all season.</p><p>- Minimum 3 consecutive nights stay required during New Year Eve&rsquo;s period (23 Dec &ndash; 04 Jan).</p>', 'Active', '1668665982_Grand Hyatt.webp', 5, 'https://www.hyatt.com/en-US/hotel/indonesia/grand-hyatt-bali/balgh?src=corp_lclb_gmb_seo_balgh', 'https://goo.gl/maps/cJV4kumAbb7pivcd6', NULL, NULL, '<p>Normal season : 72 hours prior to arrival or no show: One (01) night room charge will be applied</p><p>High / Peak season : 14 days prior to arrival or no show: One (01) night room charge will be applied.</p>', NULL, '2022-11-15 19:19:42', '2023-02-02 04:32:59'),
(29, 'St Regis Bali Resort', 'i1e0SzegcDAx69QJ4sW2Jvgps5', 'Nusa Dua', 'Kawasan Pariwisata Nusa Dua Lot S6 PO.BOX 44, 80363 Nusa Dua	,Bali, Indonesia', 'Made Parwati', '03618478111', '<p>Take in picturesque ocean views from every angle at The St. Regis Bali Resort, which overlooks a pristine beach considered the most beautiful in Nusa Dua, Bali. Indulge at our exclusive, yet subtly elegant, 5-star hotel featuring the only private villas with immediate beach access in Nusa Dua. Pamper yourself with a treatment at Iridium Spa while your children enjoy fun, supervised activities at the Children&rsquo;s Learning Center on-site here at our luxury resort. At the end of another glorious day, watch an authentic Balinese Fire Dance Ritual from the resort&rsquo;s grand staircase. Savor an international range of dining delights at our hotel restaurants before retiring to your exquisitely appointed villa, just steps from our lagoon-style swimming pool and the Bali surf. Experience it all while leaving your every need in the care of our signature 24-hour St. Regis butler service. The Bali vacation you&rsquo;ve been dreaming of awaits on the shoreline of Nusa Dua&rsquo;s finest beach at The St. Regis Bali Resort.</p>', '<p>- Free Internet Access</p><p>- Free Parking</p><p>- On-Site Restaurant</p><p>- Fitness Center</p><p>- Pool</p><p>- Spa</p><p>- Digital Key</p><p>- Digital Check-In</p><p>- Resort Property</p><p>- Laundry</p><p>- Concierge</p><p>- Meeting Facilities&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p>- Children&#39;s Learning Center</p><p>- The Beach</p><p>- Water Sports Center</p><p>- La Boutique</p>', '<p>- Daily brakfast</p><p>&nbsp;- No check out is allowed on 31 December 2022 and 1 January 2023</p>', 'Active', '1668666710_St. Regis Bali.webp', 2, 'https://thestregisresort.com-bali.com/', 'https://goo.gl/maps/9JyvTRoGGRGwFXqf8', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-11-15 19:31:50', '2023-03-30 12:20:14'),
(30, 'Como Uma Canggu', 'CirqBrabnZeg5Mw3vW0IozWBK7', 'Canggu', 'Echo Beach, Jl. Pantai Batu Mejan, Canggu, Kec. Kuta Utara, Kabupaten Badung	,Bali, Indonesia', 'Yuli Rahmayanti', '03616202209', '<p>COMO Uma Canggu is situated on Bali&#39;s south coast &mdash; a beachfront destination offering panoramic views of the soft volcanic sand and rolling waves. This luxury resort in Canggu &mdash; an area liked for its laid-back caf&eacute; scene and surf waves &mdash; offers stylish accommodation, exceptional cuisine, meaningful wellness and the same impeccable service COMO is known for across the globe. Guests can nurture their wellbeing at the resort&rsquo;s COMO Shambhala Retreat, with daily fitness classes, hands-on healing and holistic therapies. Friends and family can gather at the buzzing COMO Beach Club, where an eclectic global menu can be enjoyed to the sounds of live acoustic musicians and DJs, with some of the best sunset views on the island.</p>', '<p>- Fitness Centre</p><p>- 115m lagoon pool</p><p>- COMO the Shop</p><p>- glow</p><p>- Seven treatment rooms (five singles and -two doubles)</p><p>- Gym (250sq m)</p><p>- Two Pilates studios (51sq m and 36sq m)</p><p>- Two yoga studios (56sq m and 46sq m)</p><p>- 25m lap pool at the COMO Beach Club</p><p>- COMO Beach Club</p><p>- Play by COMO Space</p>', '<p>Daily breakfast</p>', 'Active', '1668669380_Como Uma Canggu.jpg', 2, 'https://www.comohotels.com/en/umacanggu', 'https://goo.gl/maps/vT27NyLJFzjT1ZMG8', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-11-15 20:16:20', '2023-03-30 16:21:25'),
(31, 'Como Shambala Estate', 'jFi6k9LEW1GV3TwGhUiivryhoU', 'Gianyar', 'Banjar Begawan, Desa, Melinggih Kelod, Kec. Payangan, Kabupaten Gianyar ,Bali, Indonesia', 'Yuli Rahmayanti', '0361978888', '<p>COMO Shambhala Estate is a residential retreat combining holistic wellness with exceptional villa accommodation. The location is unique, a spiritual enclave of jungle, river and sun-rich clearings just north of Ubud. Specialists in yoga and Pilates provide inspiration and nurture, working in harmony with guides for mountain biking, hiking, climbing, white-water rafting and outdoor circuit training. For lasting commitment and actionable change to take home, guests can embark on our Integrated Wellness Programme, which is tailored to individual wellness needs.</p>', '<p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Nine treatment rooms (three for couples)</p><p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Three treatment pavilions</p><p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Outdoor hydrotherapy area with vitality pool</p><p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Male/female sauna and steam room</p><p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Yoga pavilion and Yoga bale</p><p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pilates studio Consultation rooms</p><p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 25-metre swimming pool</p><p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Chemical-free natural spring water pools</p><p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Gym with weights and cardio equipment</p><p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Outdoor jungle gym</p>', '<p>*Daily breakfast</p><p>*Check-in and check out is not permitted due to Balinese silent day - Nyepi Day : Between 6:00am on 11th March 2024 and 6:00am on 12th March 2024&nbsp;</p><p>*Check out on 31st December is not permitted&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Honeymoon Amenities :&nbsp;</strong></p><p>All honeymoon guests staying for minimum 3 consecutive nights will receive with our compliments :&nbsp;</p><p>*Special welcome amenity&nbsp;</p><p>*Honeymoon set up in the room upon arrival&nbsp;</p><p>*Proof of marriage within last 6 months must be presented at the time of reservation or at the time of arrival&nbsp;</p>', 'Active', '1668671765_Como Shambala Estate.jpg', 14, 'https://www.comohotels.com/en/comoshambhalaestate', 'https://goo.gl/maps/rpcL66vjGoAUrauV6', NULL, NULL, '<p><strong>Season 1 :&nbsp;</strong></p><p>*Booking cancelled between 7 and 3 days prior to arrival date will incur cancellation charges equal: 1 night accomodation cost&nbsp;</p><p>*Booking cancelled within 3 days of the date of arrival will incur cancellation charges equal : 100% of the total booking&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Season 2 (For Individual Rooms and Suites Reservations Only) :&nbsp;</strong></p><p><b>*</b>Bookings cancelled between 14 days and 8 days prior to arrival date will incur cancellation charges equal : 1 night accomodation cost&nbsp;</p><p>*Booking cancelled within 7 days of the date of arrival will incur cancellation charges equal : 100% of the total booking</p><p><strong>Season 2 (For Residence/Villa Reservations Only) :</strong></p><p>*Booking cancelled between 60 days and 45 days prior to arrival date will incur cancellation charges equal : 1 nights accommodation cost&nbsp;</p><p>*Bookings cancelled within 44 days of the date of arrival will incur cancellation charges equal : 100% of the total booking&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Season 3 (For Individual Rooms and Suite Reservations Only) :</strong>&nbsp;</p><p>*Bookings cancelled between 45 days and 31 days prior to arrival date will incur cancellation charges equal : 1 night accommodation cost</p><p>*Bookings cancelled within 30 days of the date of arrival will incur cancellation charges equal :100% of the total booking</p><p><strong>Season 3 (For Residence/Villa Reservations Only) :&nbsp;</strong></p><p>*Booking cancelled between 60 days and 45 days prior to arrival date will incur cancellation charges equal to 1 night accommodation cost</p><p>*Bookings cancelled within 44 days of the date of arrival will incur cancellation charges equal : 100% of the total booking</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, '2022-11-15 20:56:05', '2023-06-22 04:20:38'),
(32, 'Como Uma Ubud', 'VCYvC220wmvdB8dDsnkWvWpOW1', 'Ubud', 'Jl. Raya Sanggingan Banjar Lungsiakan, Kedewatan, Kecamatan Ubud, Kabupaten Gianyar	,Bali, Indonesia', 'Yuli Rahmayanti', '0361972448', '<p>COMO Uma Ubud is a luxury resort in the heart of Ubud. The contemporary Asian design of our 46 rooms, suites and villas are relaxed, sunshine-filled spaces. Our restaurants, Kemiri and Uma Cucina, boast world-class cuisine while COMO Shambhala Retreat at Uma Ubud focuses on holistic wellness, with active pursuits including temple visits, biking and trekking.</p>', '<p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp; como shambhala retreat wellness facilities: yoga studio, yoga pavilion, pool, gym, four treatment rooms</p><p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp; room services: daily housekeeping, laundry</p><p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp; complimentary scheduled shuttle to and from ubud town</p><p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp; services upon request: personal shopping, babysitting</p><p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp; como the shop retail boutique</p><p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp; concierge service to arrange airport transfers, daily tours and more</p><p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp; restaurants and bar: uma cucina, kemiri, uma bar</p><p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp; daily scheduled activities and guided walks to join</p><p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp; meeting room facilities and catering service for event</p>', '<p>Daily breakfast</p>', 'Active', '1682318385_Como Uma Ubud.jpg', 2, 'https://www.comohotels.com/en/umaubud', 'https://goo.gl/maps/FFR7GVLf3M911nq97', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-11-15 21:29:20', '2023-04-23 23:39:45'),
(33, 'Movenpick Resort', 'pHBsgVWtjQ7lRkmtl8VmZa2T3V', 'Jimbaran', 'Jl. Wanagiri No.1, Jimbaran, Kec. Kuta Sel., Kabupaten Badung ,Bali, Indonesia', 'Thalia Susanti', '03614725777', '<p>Immerse yourself in island living, a vibrant culinary scene and Balinese wellness at M&ouml;venpick Resort &amp; Spa Jimbaran Bali, a 5-star family resort less than 5 minutes walk from Jimbaran Beach. Relax at the pool with swim-up hammocks or unwind with a massage at our traditional Arkipela Spa.</p><p>Shop at Samasta Lifestyle Village while your children are having fun in our pirate-themed Meera Kids Club.</p>', '<p>- Free Internet Access</p><p>- Free Parking</p><p>- Restaurant</p><p>- Fitness Center</p><p>- Pool</p><p>- Spa</p><p>- Digital Key</p><p>- Digital Check-In</p><p>- Resort Property</p><p>- Laundry</p><p>- Concierge</p><p>- Meeting Facilities</p>', '<p>- Daily breakfast</p><p>- Minimum 3&nbsp;nights stay booking&nbsp;over 30 and 31 December.</p>', 'Active', '1668674724_Movenpick Bali.webp', 2, 'https://www.movenpick.com/en/asia/indonesia/bali/jimbaran-bali.html', 'https://g.page/movenpick-bali?share', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-11-15 21:45:24', '2023-04-23 23:49:49'),
(35, 'Holiday Inn Resort Baruna', '7VRlceqe4DrZ2YeatHZhG7neWv', 'Kuta', 'Jl. Wana Segara No.33, Tuban, Kec. Kuta, Kabupaten Badung, Bali 80361', 'Aven Tarigan', '0361755577', '<p>Situated on a tranquil oasis in South Kuta, Bali, beachfront Holiday Inn Resort Baruna Bali is located 10 minutes away from Denpasar International Airport and 15 minutes away from the excitement of downtown. Our resort offers you a family-friendly stay with fun-filled activities and child-friendly facilities.</p><p>Everything around you invites you to relax. Revel in the cozy embrace of our 193 contemporary style guest rooms and suites. Each is equipped with a private balcony overlooking the breathtaking Indian Ocean or the lush of natural surroundings, while the comfortable chaise lounges allow you to spend long hours to soak up refreshing island breeze.</p>', '<p>- Free Internet Access</p><p>- Free Parking</p><p>- Restaurant</p><p>- Fitness Center</p><p>- Pool</p><p>- Spa</p><p>- Digital Key</p><p>- Digital Check-In</p><p>- Resort Property</p><p>- Laundry</p><p>- Concierge</p><p>- Meeting Facilities&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>', '<ul><li>Daily breakfast</li><li>Minimum 3 nights stay&nbsp;on 30th &amp; 31st December 2022 (New Year), No check out on 31 Dec 2022 allowed.</li><li>No compulsory Dinner during Christmas and New Year.</li></ul>', 'Draft', '1668741411_Holiday Inn Resort Baruna.jpg', 5, 'https://www.ihg.com/holidayinnresorts/hotels/us/en/bali/dpsbh/hoteldetail?cm_mmc=GoogleMaps-_-RS-_-I', 'https://g.page/HolidayInnResortBarunaBali?share', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-11-16 16:16:51', '2022-11-19 19:46:09'),
(36, 'Holiday Inn Express Baruna', 'iYCuv63Ny52Gnl0DYLLVLMrqoy', 'Kuta', 'Jl. Wana Segara No.33A, Tuban, Bali, Kabupaten Badung, Bali', 'Aven Tarigan', '0361755585', '<p>Each modern and comfortable room at Holiday Inn Express Baruna Bali is equipped with air conditioning, a flat-screen cable TV, wardrobe, refrigerator, and an ergonomic desk. The private bathroom includes a powerful shower, hairdryer and free toiletries. Fresh towels and bed linen are also provided in the rooms and free breakfast is provided daily.</p>', '<p>- Free Internet Access</p><p>- Free Parking</p><p>- Restaurant</p><p>- Fitness Center</p><p>- Pool</p><p>- Spa</p><p>- Digital Key</p><p>- Digital Check-In</p><p>- Laundry</p><p>- Concierge</p><p>- Meeting Facilities&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>', '<ul><li>Daily breakfast</li><li>Minimum 3 nights stay&nbsp;on 30th &amp; 31st December 2022 (New Year), No check out on 31 Dec 2022 allowed.</li><li>No compulsory Dinner during Christmas and New Year.</li></ul>', 'Draft', '1668742701_holiday-inn-express-bali.jpg', 5, 'https://www.ihg.com/holidayinnexpress/hotels/us/en/reservation', 'https://goo.gl/maps/PzDDxSW6h8cNYxFc7', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-11-16 16:38:21', '2022-11-19 19:46:30'),
(37, 'Mayaloka Villa', '60jtYgRkHOUJUKBIHrgNEBxfqJ', 'Seminyak', 'Jl. Cendrawasih Jl. Petitenget No.88, Seminyak, Kec. Kuta Utara, Kabupaten Badung	,Bali, Indonesia', '(Ms) Ayu', '03614736436', '<p>An awarded certificate of excellent and travel choice 2020 by Tripadvisor, Mayaloka offers open air concept Boutique Villas with authentic Balinese architecture design experience.</p><p>Our villa offers complete privacy with its own private entrance, whilst having the added benefit of a 24-hour front office for anything you may need.</p>', '<p>- Free Internet Access</p><p>- Free Parking</p><p>- Restaurant</p><p>- Fitness Center</p><p>- Pool</p><p>- Spa</p><p>- Digital Key</p><p>- Digital Check-In</p><p>- Resort Property</p><p>- Laundry</p><p>- Concierge</p><p>- Meeting Facilities</p>', '<ul><li>Daily breakfast</li><li>Special bookings made in Peak Season, for arrivals between 20 December and 5 January should be for minimum of 3 night&rsquo;s stay.</li></ul>', 'Draft', '1668742972_Mayaloka Villa.jpg', 5, 'https://mayaresorts.com/', 'https://goo.gl/maps/7TZ1CdN5V91Xm674A', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-11-16 16:42:52', '2022-11-19 19:49:42'),
(38, 'Aston Canggu Beach Resort', 'g4qWS0UeWfkupi37Qqv5Wu1bYr', 'Canggu', 'Jl. Pantai Batu Bolong No.99, Canggu, Kec. Kuta Utara, Kabupaten Badung	,Bali, Indonesia', '(Ms) Yuni', '03613023333', '<p>ASTON Canggu Beach Resort is a perfect home in Canggu &nbsp;located just a walk away from the famous surfing point at Batu Bolong Beach. Our Hotel feature a rooftop dining venue, UpZscale Sky Dining &amp; Bar, which lies by the poolside, overlooks the majestic ocean view and spectacular sunset.&nbsp;</p>', '<p>- Restaurant</p><p>- Coffee Shop</p><p>- Room Service</p><p>- Swimming Pool</p><p>- Kids Pool</p><p>- Carpark</p><p>- Wifi Area</p><p>- Spa</p><p>- Gym/Fitness Center</p><p>- Non Smoking Room</p><p>- Connecting Rooms</p><p>- Rooftop Terrace</p><p>- Safety Deposit Box</p><p>- WheelChair Access</p><p>- 24 Hour Front Desk</p><p>- 24 Hour Security</p><p>- Airport Transfer</p><p>- Laundry Service</p><p>- Luggage Storage</p>', '<p>Daily breakfast</p>', 'Draft', '1668752254_aston-canggu-beach-resort.jpg', 5, 'https://www.astonhotelsinternational.com/en/hotel/view/57/aston-canggu-beach-resort', 'https://g.page/AstonCanggu?share', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-11-16 19:17:34', '2022-11-16 19:17:34'),
(39, 'Plataran Canggu Bali Resort', 'TaE7vlxGwxd8WZkKkiRLnryLVP', 'Canggu', 'Jalan Pengubugan Banjar, Jl. Silayukti, Kerobokan, Kec. Kuta Utara, Kabupaten Badung	,Bali, Indonesia', 'Wahyu Dwi', '0361411388', '<p>Cocooned within tropical gardens, alongside a river and lush green paddy fields, Plataran Canggu Bali Resort &amp; Spa is an oasis of amazing peace and tranquility &ndash; a secret hideaway disturbed only by the twitter of birdsong and the crickets&rsquo; hum. A delightful piece of forgotten Bali and authentic Balinese village life that lies just steps from the main street of Canggu, yet feels far removed from the madding crowd.</p><p>Plataran Canggu&rsquo;s landscape, designed in the form of a labyrinth, is the legacy of the late renowned landscape architect &ndash; Made Wijaya This unique structure allows guests to wander off and explore the ultimate privacy and serenity of the resort.</p><p>From the 250-year-old Joglo structure at reception to the traditional alang-alang roofed villas with antique carved doorways, Indonesia&rsquo;s rich architectural heritage provides an exotic setting for life&rsquo;s finest comforts and experiences. Discover the true essence of Bali in sensual spa rituals, exceptional cuisine, and in the rich tapestry of cultural and spiritual traditions that are central to the rhythm of Bali life. Lose yourself in a truly exotic Balinese experience.</p>', '<p>- Aurora Deck</p><p>- Mini Jungle</p><p>- Tigadari Snack Bar</p><p>- Swimming Pools</p><p>- The Spa</p><p>- Wellness</p><p>- Wolly Kids Club &amp; Games Centre</p><p>- Sarasvati Concept Store</p><p>- Guest Services<br />&nbsp;<br />- Transportation</p><p>- Resort Facilities Map</p>', '<ul><li>Daily breakfast</li><li>No check out allowed during the date of 31st December of the ongoing year and 1st January of the following year</li></ul>', 'Draft', '1668752747_Plataran Canggu.jpg', 5, 'https://www.plataran.com/plataran-canggu/', 'https://g.page/platarancanggu?share', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-11-16 19:25:47', '2022-11-19 19:57:45'),
(40, 'Karma Kandara', 'rL5oVBpwwnzwlpBJQ9I8vojFHv', 'Ungasan', 'Jl. Villa Kandara, Banjar Wijaya Kusuma, Ungasan, Kec. Kuta Sel., Kabupaten Badung	,Bali, Indonesia', 'Yuli Undayani', '03618482200', '<p>A Luxury Cliff Top Resort with Direct Access to a Stunning Beach</p><p>Discover the essence of Karma at Karma Kandara on Bali&rsquo;s Bukit Peninsula, known globally as &lsquo;Billionaire&rsquo;s Row&rsquo;.<br />It&rsquo;s the ultimate destination for intimate groups or larger gatherings of family and friends, drawn by Bali&rsquo;s beauty and captivated by the spirit of Karma Kandara.</p>', '<p>- 3 Monkeys Kid&#39;s Club</p><p>- Watersports</p><p>- Gym</p><p>- Activities</p><p>- Karma Beach Bali</p><p>- Free Internet Access</p><p>- Free Parking</p><p>- On-Site Restaurant</p><p>- Fitness Center</p><p>- Pool</p><p>- Spa</p><p>- Digital Key</p><p>- Digital Check-In</p><p>- Resort Property</p><p>- Laundry</p><p>- Concierge</p><p>- Meeting Facilities</p>', '<p>- Daily breakfast</p><p>- The compulsory new year&#39;s eve dinner is included in the villa rate when booked with guests staying a minimum of 3 nights, however is only for 2 guests for each villa category, additional per person costs are as per contract&nbsp;rates</p><p>- No Departure on 31 December 2022</p>', 'Draft', '1668753338_Karma Kandara.jpg', 2, 'https://karmagroup.com/find-destination/karma-resorts/karma-kandara/', 'https://goo.gl/maps/58SDRS62feQtmeca8', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-11-16 19:35:38', '2023-06-16 08:55:04'),
(41, 'Six Senses Uluwatu', 'ywRQbbtyr6l0qSmyldkBynbo3f', 'Uluwatu', 'Jl. Goa Lempeh, Uluwatu, Kec. Kuta Sel., Kabupaten Badung ,Bali, Indonesia', 'Nurullita Suhandini', '03612090300', '<p>Discover us on top of the cliffs at the southernmost tip of Bali where the site of Pura Uluwatu is located, the sacred temple considered one of the island&rsquo;s core spiritual pillars. Here at our Uluwatu resort, tradition mixes with beautiful beaches, great surf breaks and an eclectic wellness and dining scene. Oh, and did we mention the uninterrupted ocean views from every aspect?</p>', '<p>- Free Internet Access</p><p>- Free Parking</p><p>- Restaurant</p><p>- Fitness Center</p><p>- Pool</p><p>- Spa</p><p>- Digital Key</p><p>- Digital Check-In</p><p>- Resort Property</p><p>- Laundry</p><p>- Concierge</p><p>- Meeting Facilities&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />&nbsp;</p>', '<p>- Daily breakfast</p><p>- No check-out on 31st December &amp; 01st January</p><p>- Gala Dinner 31st December is Non- compulsory</p>', 'Active', '1668754343_Six sense Uluwatu.webp', 2, 'https://www.sixsenses.com/en/resorts/uluwatu-bali', 'https://goo.gl/maps/ngHJyQbt89ZSMcp87', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-11-16 19:52:23', '2023-04-24 01:13:05'),
(42, 'Renaissance Bali Nusa Dua', '7qwMR9kzrS2AhZmKfm0CVJrtoV', 'Nusa Dua', 'Kawasan Pariwisata Lot SW 4 & 5, Nusa Dua Bali, Bali 80363', 'Irawan Hadiwijaya', '03612092888', '<p>Perched on the hilly area of Indonesia&#39;s Southern Bali Peninsula, Renaissance Bali Nusa Dua Resort enjoys a bird-eye view of the Nusa Dua enclave and sparkling sea. Inspired by Balinese theater, our resort is fashioned for all senses in theatrical lifestyle and design elements. All rooms and suites boast spacious areas with plush bedding, private balconies, fashionable living areas and bathrooms with soaking tubs. Delight your palate at our distinctive restaurants, including a beach club and an authentic Indonesian restaurant, Nusantara by Locavore. Our resort houses modern meeting rooms, including a grand ballroom that is ideal for your unconventional gala. Pamper your senses with an indulgent spa treatment after a day of island discovery and beach hopping. Little ones will love the Lava Land Kids Club with kids pool, next to resort&rsquo;s outdoor pools with pool bar. Explore Indonesia from Renaissance Bali Nusa Dua Resort with your R Navigator, where unforgettable adventure awaits.</p>', '<p>- Restaurant</p><p>- Fitness Center</p><p>- Spa</p><p>- Outdoor Pool</p><p>- Hot Tub</p><p>- Meeting Space</p><p>- Free Wifi</p><p>- Activities for Kids</p><p>- Bicycle Rental</p><p>- Game Room</p><p>- Convenience Store</p><p>- Dry Cleaning Service</p><p>- Laundry</p><p>- Hair salon</p><p>- Room Service</p><p>- 24 Hour Room Service</p><p>- Wake up Calls</p><p>- Daily Housekeeping</p><p>- Turndown Service</p><p>- Service Reques</p>', '<p>Daily breakfast</p><p>Minimum 3 night stay for booking stay over 30 - 31 December</p>', 'Draft', '1682327797_atomic-17-pool.jpg', 2, 'https://www.marriott.com/en-us/hotels/dpsnd-renaissance-bali-nusa-dua-resort/overview', 'https://goo.gl/maps/WgHGHbSmiE3WbEFCA', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-11-19 17:13:20', '2023-05-31 03:24:52'),
(43, 'Revivo Wellness Resort Bali', 'tuVJaAXP4TPjNIsO1CjC4si1ZD', 'Nusa Dua', 'Jalan Desa Sawangan, Benoa, Kec. Kuta Sel., Kabupaten Badung, Bali, Indonesia', 'Rosila Anton', '03614773888', '<p>REVV Wellness Resorts are sustainable wellness hotels offering comprehensive, personalised retreats teaching self-awareness, mindfulness and different practices that ensure mind-body balance, vitality and happiness.</p><p>Each property provides a range of wellness programs inspired by local ancient healing traditions and designed to maintain or improve specific emotional, physical, and mental health conditions. REVV Wellness Retreats aspire to be a holistic transformational experience that is tailor-made and results-driven.</p>', '<p>- Free Internet Access</p><p>- Free Parking</p><p>- Restaurant</p><p>- Fitness Center</p><p>- Pool</p><p>- Spa</p><p>- Digital Key</p><p>- Digital Check-In</p><p>- Resort Property</p><p>- Laundry</p><p>- Concierge</p><p>- Meeting Facilities&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Daily breakfast</p>', 'Draft', '1669005013_Revivo Bali.jpg', 5, 'https://www.revivoresorts.com/', 'https://g.page/revivoresorts?share', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-11-19 17:30:13', '2022-11-19 17:30:13'),
(44, 'The Ritz Carlton Bali', 'JDzVfZvcsf0Eijx2YRyqJGr1mB', 'Nusa Dua', 'Jl. Raya Nusa Dua Selatan, Lot Iii, Sawangan, Nusa Dua ,Bali, Indonesia', 'Kelwin Lim', '03618498988', '<p>Every detail of The Ritz-Carlton, Bali experience is inspired by the beauty and allure of the ocean. Overlooking the beach in Nusa Dua, this luxury resort celebrates its Bali surroundings at every moment. Luxury resort villas feature private pools, lush gardens and breathtaking views. The hotel&#39;s glass-enclosed wedding chapel is a modern interpretation of a classic structure. Meals at the resort are accompanied by an ocean breeze.</p>', '<p>- Free Internet Access</p><p>- Free Parking</p><p>- Restaurant</p><p>- Fitness Center</p><p>- Pool</p><p>- Spa</p><p>- Digital Key</p><p>- Digital Check-In</p><p>- Resort Property</p><p>- Laundry</p><p>- Concierge</p><p>- Meeting Facilities&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />&nbsp;</p>', '<p>- Daily breakfast</p><p>- Complimentary access to Ritz Kids (signature kids club) for children during stay in the hotel</p><p>- Minimum stay of four (4) nights applies for arrivals between 28 December&ndash; 1 January</p><p>- No check out allowed on 31 December</p><p>- No compulsory New Year&rsquo;s Eve dinner apply</p>', 'Active', '1669015924_The Ritz-Carlton Bali.jpg', 2, 'https://www.ritzcarlton.com/en/hotels/indonesia/bali', 'https://g.page/ritzcarltonbali?share', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-11-19 20:32:04', '2023-04-24 02:39:40'),
(45, 'The Westin Resort', '2xourj1tcneyUFQa7npoGmtL10', 'Nusa Dua', 'Kawasan Pariwisata Nusa Dua, ITDC Lot N-3, Nusa Dua, Bali, Indonesia, 80363', 'Praba Kusumasari', '0361771906', '<p>Nestled on the white sand beaches of the Indian Ocean, The Westin Resort Nusa Dua, Bali is a contemporary hotel in a 5-star setting. Our balanced hotel appeals to business travelers and vacationers alike with our warm accommodations and proximity to the Bali International Convention Center located just next door. Our lush, perfectly groomed resort grounds offer a serene Balinese sanctuary by the beach. Enjoy a revitalizing treatment at our wellness day spa or relax, drink in hand, by our sparkling freshwater pool. Dine at our six onsite restaurants for a casual or upscale dining experience you won&#39;t soon forget. Stay active with a number of recreational activities including a variety of exhilarating watersports, two Westin tennis courts and our Westin Family KidsClub. Each of our refined guestrooms features our signature Heavenly Beds, elevated amenities and private balcony with either garden or ocean views. Whatever your reason for travel, our goal is to ensure you leave feeling better than when you arrive.</p>', '<p>&bull; restaurant<br />&bull; fitness center<br />&bull; spa<br />&bull; outdoor pool<br />&bull; meeting space<br />&bull; activities for kids<br />&bull; beach access<br />&bull; Convenience store<br />&bull; Gift shop<br />&bull; Dry cleaning service<br />&bull; Laundry<br />&bull; kitchen<br />&bull; Room service<br />&bull; Daily housekeeping<br />&bull; Turndown service</p>', '<p>&bull; Daily breakfast<br />&bull; Minimum 4 night stay during 24th December 2023 &ndash; 5th January 2024<br />&bull; Minimum 2 night stay during 09-17 February 2024 (Chinese New Year)<br />&bull; New Year Eve Gala Dinner is compulsory<br />&bull; No check-out &nbsp;on 31 December, will allow check-in 31 December with NYE dinner</p>', 'Active', '1669018968_westin-nusa-dua-bali.jpg', 1