(46, 'Hyatt Regency Bali', 'R5oh6SOgMxhTNYNXDVCDtOkiFV', 'Sanur', 'Jalan Danau Tamblingan 89, Sanur,80228	,Bali, Indonesia', 'Iin Sari', '0361281234', '<p>Spend your staycation at Hyatt Regency Bali, a beachfront hotel in Sanur built on nine hectares of lush tropical gardens. Relax in the comfort of one of our 363 rooms, or swim in one of our three swimming pools. With plenty of things to do in the resort and outside, your staycation will be a memorable and restful break. The hotel is conveniently located near Bali&rsquo;s main tourist attractions, and the International Airport Ngurah Rai is just 16 km away.</p><p>Hyatt Regency Bali is a CHSE certified and GBAC STARTM accredited hotel.</p>', '<p>- Free Internet Access</p><p>- Free Parking</p><p>- On-Site Restaurant</p><p>- Fitness Center</p><p>- Pool</p><p>- Spa</p><p>- Digital Key</p><p>- Digital Check-In</p><p>- Camp Hyatt</p><p>- Resort Property</p><p>- Laundry</p><p>- Concierge</p><p>- Meeting Facilities&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>', '<p><b>Standard benefit :</b></p><p>Daily breakfast</p><p><b>Seasonal policy :</b></p><p>Minimum 2 consecutive nights stay required for all season.</p><p>Minimum 3 consecutive nights stay required during New Year Eve&rsquo;s period (23 Dec &ndash; 04 Jan).</p>', 'Active', '1669177523_Hyatt-Regency-Bali.webp', 2, 'https://www.hyatt.com/', 'https://g.page/hyattregencybali?share', NULL, NULL, '<p>* Normal season : 72 hours prior to arrival or no show: One (01) night room charge will be applied</p><p>* High / Peak season : 14 days prior to arrival or no show: One (01) night room charge will be applied.</p>', NULL, '2022-11-21 17:25:23', '2023-06-16 09:02:35'),
(47, 'Maya Sanur Resort & Spa', 'QR1PCpUOq8Bh5IAJrUaERo2YeC', 'Sanur', 'Jalan Danau Tamblingan, PO Box 3253, Sanur	,Bali, Indonesia', 'Wilaca', '623618497800', '<p>Step from lush tropical gardens onto white-sand beach and feel the gentle caress of the sea breeze as you tread the boardwalk of this former fishing village. From the moment you arrive, contemporary flourishes are counter-balanced by iconic Balinese design elements.</p>', '<p>- Free Internet Access</p><p>- Free Parking</p><p>- Restaurant</p><p>- Fitness Center</p><p>- Pool</p><p>- Spa</p><p>- Digital Key</p><p>- Digital Check-In</p><p>- Resort Property</p><p>- Laundry</p><p>- Concierge</p><p>- Meeting Facilities</p>', '<p>* Daily breakfast</p><p>*&nbsp; Minimum 2 nights stay is required on December 22, 2022 &ndash; January 02, 2023</p><p>*&nbsp; No check-out is allowed on December 31, 2022</p><p>*&nbsp; There are no compulsory meal plans during the high season periods or during the year-end festive season.</p>', 'Draft', '1669186026_Maya Sanur.webp', 2, 'https://mayaresorts.com/sanur', 'https://g.page/mayasanur?share', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-11-21 19:47:06', '2023-06-16 09:08:48'),
(48, 'Sudamala Resort Sanur', 'FwFJV6ScppTqHvlD4HLHMpM5Uh', 'Sanur', 'Jl. Sudamala No.20, Sanur Kauh, Denpasar Selatan, Bali, Indonesia', 'Putri Eka', '0361288555', '<p>If you seek an authentic encounter with the real Bali and yearn to sojourn where art lives, search no more. Situated at the southern end of serene Sanur, Bali&rsquo;s cultured pearl and oft-kept secret, Sudamala Suites &amp; Villas is an oasis for those who crave a refined retreat that melds world-renowned Balinese artistry and craftsmanship with mind-boggling attention to detail and timeless tropical modern luxury.</p>', '<ul><li>Free Internet Access</li><li>Free Parking</li><li>On-Site Restaurant</li><li>Fitness Center</li><li>Water Sport</li><li>Pool</li><li>Spa</li><li>Digital Key</li><li>Digital Check-In</li><li>Resort Property</li><li>Laundry</li><li>Concierge</li><li>Meeting Facilities&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</li></ul>', '<p>*Daily breakfast</p><p>*No check out on 31 December&nbsp;</p><p>*Minimum stay of three (3) consecutive nights is required during peak season period on 24 December - 03 January</p><p><strong>Honeymoon &amp; Anniversary :&nbsp;</strong></p><p>*Honeymooner guests are given special Flower Decor on bed (standard room) OR Flower petals in the bathtub in the room (highest room category) on their arrival date.&nbsp;</p>', 'Active', '1669255364_Sudamala SANUR.jpg', 14, 'https://www.sudamalaresorts.com/', 'https://goo.gl/maps/tJ4Q56CJ2jxiidv2A', NULL, NULL, '<p><strong>Low, Shoulder Season :&nbsp;</strong></p><p>*Cancellation within 14-04 days prior to arrival : 1 night&#39;s charge&nbsp;</p><p>*Cancellation within 03-01 days prior to arrival : full charge of total room night reserved&nbsp;</p><p><strong>High Season :&nbsp;</strong></p><p>*Cancellation within 30-15 days prior to arrival : 1 night&#39;s charge&nbsp;</p><p>*Cancellation within 14-08 days prior to arrival : 50% charge of total room night reserved&nbsp;</p><p>*Cancellation within 07-01 days prior to arrival : full charge of 