(49, 'Komaneka at Keramas Beach', 'r9dqZdRo0AYu8gfeE1yWMi6PLU', 'Gianyar', 'Jalan Prof. Ida Bagus Mantra, Keramas 80581	,Bali, Indonesia', 'Bagus Pramana', '0361705777', '<p>Komaneka Resorts is founded, designed, and run by young Balinese couple from Ubud, Koman W. Suteja and Mansri Trisniawati. Firstly introduced as an art gallery specializing in high-end Balinese and Indonesian contemporary art, Komaneka is a collection of boutique resorts - each carefully created to fulfill travelers&#39; expectations of upscale luxury lifestyle, surrounded by Ubud&#39;s natural beauty or the dramatic seaside of Keramas. Designed to reflect a contemporary interpretation of traditional Balinese style and architecture, you will also be looked after by our gracious professional staff, with utmost attention to details for your ultimate Bali experience. Experience the excitement of Bali&#39;s cultural heritage. Choose a Komaneka resort for your home address in Bali</p>', '<ul><li>Free Internet Access</li><li>Free Parking</li><li>On-Site Restaurant</li><li>Fitness Center</li><li>Pool</li><li>Spa</li><li>Digital Key</li><li>Digital Check-In</li><li>Resort Property</li><li>Laundry</li><li>Concierge</li><li>Meeting Facilities</li></ul>', '<p><strong>Standard Benefit :&nbsp;</strong></p><ul><li>Daily breakfast</li><li>Daily afternoon tea with Balinese and Western cakes</li></ul><p><strong>Children Policy :&nbsp;</strong></p><ul><li>0-2 year&#39;s old baby cot is free of charge&nbsp;</li><li>3-5 year&#39;s old sharing bed with parent inclusive of breakfast is free of charge&nbsp;</li></ul><p><strong>Honeymoon Benefit :</strong>&nbsp;</p><ul><li>Honeymoon cake</li><li>Honeymoon set up in the room&nbsp;</li><li>Fruits upon arrival&nbsp;</li></ul><p><strong>Seasonal Policy :&nbsp;</strong></p><ul><li>No check in/check out on Nyepi Day (11 March 2024)</li><li>Min. 2 nights stay during peak season period (24 Dec 2023 - 06 Jan 2024)&nbsp;</li></ul>', 'Draft', '1669258489_Komaneka at Keramas Beach.jpg', 14, 'https://www.komaneka.com/keramas', 'https://g.page/komanekaatkeramasbeach?share', NULL, NULL, '<p><strong>Normal Season :&nbsp;</strong></p><ul><li>Cancellation within 14 days of arrival : 1 night charge&nbsp;</li><li>Cancellation within 7 days of arrival : full charge&nbsp;</li></ul><p><strong>High Season </strong>(01 July - 31 Aug 2023) :&nbsp;</p><ul><li>Cancellation within 21 days of arrival : 1 night charge&nbsp;</li><li>Cancellation within 14 days of arrival : full charge&nbsp;</li></ul><p><strong>Peak Season</strong> (24 Dec 2023 - 06 Jan 2024) :&nbsp;</p><ul><li>Cancellation within 30 days of arrival : full charge&nbsp;</li></ul><p><strong>No Show :</strong> 100% room charge&nbsp;</p>', NULL, '2022-11-22 15:54:50', '2023-07-05 06:57:34'),
(50, 'Komaneka at Monkey Forest', 'TTnlUlFLCweLK9XvKeJq41SAei', 'Ubud', 'Jl. Monkey Forest, Ubud, Kecamatan Ubud, Kabupaten Gianyar, Bali 80571', 'Bagus Pramana', '03614792518', '<p>Komaneka at Monkey Forest began as a residence for artists behind the prestigious Komaneka Gallery, specializing in fine contemporary Indonesian and Balinese art. Now recently renovated with luxurious suites, an infinity pool, open-air restaurant, spa, and pool villas, all in a lush garden with mature shade trees, this is a very special oasis.<br />The resort&#39;s location on the Monkey Forest Road gives immediate access to the Ubud market and all the cultural activities of the Ubud palace, Puri Ubud, residence of Ubud&#39;s ruling family. At the other end of this bustling street, lined with restaurants and boutiques, is a sacred monkey forest.</p>', '<p>&bull; Dining<br />&bull; Garden Terrace Kitchen<br />&bull; Spa<br />&nbsp;</p>', '<ul><li>Daily Breakfast</li><li>Daily Afternoon Tea with Balinese and Western Cakes</li></ul>', 'Draft', '1669259170_komaneka at monkey forest.jpg', 5, 'https://www.komaneka.com/monkeyforest', 'https://goo.gl/maps/Trh8fbh5W86jQ7gr6', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-11-22 16:06:11', '2022-11-27 16:41:19'),
(51, 'Hideaway Villas Bali Uluwatu', 'AE3HvMFJHlJXr4Xid1F9FnCTrY', 'Uluwatu', 'Uluwatu, Jl. Bangbang Bendot, Pecatu, South Kuta, Badung Regency, Bali 80361', 'Febby Prilia', '03614725455', '<p>Set in the lush seclusion of Bali&rsquo;s Rustic Bukit Peninsula in Uluwatu, Hideaway Villas Bali Uluwatu under the management of Kanaan Hospitality caters to a rejuvenation haven for the soul, as well as total comfort for the mind. Situated in a stunningly secluded area in Uluwatu, a mere 40-minute away from Ngurah Rai International Airport (DPS), within a 10-minute drive leads to Garuda Wisnu Kencana and Pura Luhur Uluwatu, and surrounded by some of the famous beaches in Bali.</p>', '<p>&bull; Bas&eacute; restaurant<br />&bull; Bamboo Spa<br />&bull; Gym</p>', '<p>Daily breakfast</p>', 'Draft', '1669607148_Hideaway Uluwatu.jpg', 5, 'https://hideawayvillasbali.com/', 'https://g.page/hideawayvillasbali?share', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-11-26 16:45:49', '2022-11-26 16:45:49'),
(52, 'Adiwana Resort Jembawan', 'xEIPy4hpf4CFhuMs4YAQvqQCDM', 'Ubud', 'Jl. Jembawan, Ubud, Kecamatan Ubud, Kabupaten Gianyar, Bali 80571', 'Deni Asih', '03619083289', '<p>Adiwana Resort Jembawan is a boutique wellness retreat in the heart of Ubud that focuses on body, mind and spirit of rejuvenation. With its team of onsite experts, including an Ayurvedic practitioner and yoga instructor, the resort offers lifestyle programs that are tailored to address any specific health concerns you may have. Designed by Ground Kent Architect, based in Perth, the spacious rooms and suites are built with contemporary Bali in mind.&nbsp;</p>', '<p>- Free Internet Access</p><p>- Free Parking</p><p>- Restaurant</p><p>- Fitness Center</p><p>- Pool</p><p>- Spa</p><p>- Digital Key</p><p>- Digital Check-In</p><p>- Resort Property</p><p>- Laundry</p><p>- Concierge</p><p>- Meeting Facilities&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p>- INFINITY POOL</p><p>- HERB LIBRARY</p>', '<ul><li>Daily breakfast</li><li>Daily afternoon tea</li><li>No Check in and Check Out on &ndash; seclusion day (Nyepi Day)</li><li>Minimum 2 Nights stay is applicable for check in during period 24,25, 30,31 December</li></ul>', 'Draft', '1669609756_Adiwana Jembawan.jpg', 5, 'https://adiwanahotels.com/jembawan-resort-ubud-bali/', 'https://goo.gl/maps/HsVYfNgctqsFFFqm7', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-11-26 17:29:16', '2022-11-26 17:56:50'),
(53, 'Adiwana Bisma', '3vuMEEc1odi7VcI9tPkXwM3ZJp', 'Ubud', 'Jl. Bisma, Ubud, Kecamatan Ubud, Kabupaten Gianyar, Bali 80571', 'Suadita', '03616202008', '<p>Welcome to Adiwana Bisma Ubud, a luxuriously stylish boutique hotel set in the heart of Bali&rsquo;s cultural hub. A peaceful oasis just steps away from the Monkey Forest, our hotel offers the very best in Balinese hospitality amidst a refined and uplifting atmosphere. Guests are welcomed into a serene and elegant retreat, complete with beautifully designed bedrooms, exceptional facilities and beautiful surroundings. Innovative and imaginative dining is available at Pistachio restaurant featuring all the flavours of the island, while head-to-toe pampering awaits at our award-winning Tejas Spa. Soak up the sun at our rooftop infinity pool or enjoy a romantic escapade for two. Exciting activities await whether you choose to remain in the hotel or explore the very best of Ubud.</p>', '<p>- INFINITY POOL BAR</p><p>- Free Internet Access</p><p>- Free Parking</p><p>- Restaurant</p><p>- Fitness Center</p><p>- Pool</p><p>- Spa</p><p>- Digital Key</p><p>- Digital Check-In</p><p>- Resort Property</p><p>- Laundry</p><p>- Concierge</p><p>- Meeting Facilities&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>', '<ul><li>Daily breakfast</li><li>Daily afternoon tea</li><li>No Check In and Check Out on &ndash; seclusion day (Nyepi Day)</li><li>Minimum 2 Nights stay is applicable for check in during period 24,25, 30,31 December</li></ul>', 'Draft', '1669611123_Adiwana Bisma.jpg', 5, 'https://adiwanahotels.com/bisma-resort-ubud-bali/', 'https://goo.gl/maps/SaxkVaCx362vdvuEA', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-11-26 17:52:03', '2022-11-26 17:52:03'),
(54, 'Adiwana Monkey Forest', 'iVSvH97DCVKPGPiOCVcbOJ9vfl', 'Ubud', 'Monkey Forest, Street Jalan Wenara Wana, Ubud, Kecamatan Ubud, Kabupaten Gianyar, Bali 80571', 'Mr. Bayu', '0361975231', '<p>The Monkey Forest area has always been referred to as the beating heart of Ubud. It captures the essence of Tri Hita Karana that believes that in order to reach the ultimate well-being, one must live harmoniously with other people, with nature, and with God. Strategically located within the area, Adiwana Monkey Forest offers the perfect Bali getaway. The 21 suites are beautifully designed to showcase the artistic Balinese craftsmanship while maintaining a contemporary feel.&nbsp;</p>', '<p>- Free Internet Access</p><p>- Free Parking</p><p>- Restaurant</p><p>- Fitness Center</p><p>- Pool</p><p>- Spa</p><p>- Digital Key</p><p>- Digital Check-In</p><p>- Resort Property</p><p>- Laundry</p><p>- Concierge</p><p>- Meeting Facilities&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>', '<ul><li>Daily breakfast</li><li>Daily afternoon tea</li><li>No Check In and Check Out on &ndash; seclusion day (Nyepi Day)</li><li>Minimum 2 Nights stay is applicable for check in during period 24,25, 30,31 December</li></ul>', 'Draft', '1669612653_Adiwana Monkey Forest.jpg', 5, 'https://adiwanahotels.com/monkey-forest-resort-ubud-bali/', 'https://goo.gl/maps/3651dBsUHYmEF7GP9', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-11-26 18:17:33', '2022-11-26 18:17:33'),
(55, 'Capella Ubud', 'wDof2qHDqUZjNRs5KN14VtMy0t', 'Ubud', 'Jl. RY Dalem, Keliki, Kec. Tegallalang, Kabupaten Gianyar, Bali 80561', 'Isma Suryani', '03612091888', '<p>Nestled in the heart of lush green forests, our unique tented camp sits in harmony with the surrounding nature. Inspired by the early European settlers from the 1800s, architect Bill Bensley designed Capella Ubud, Bali as a tribute to their spirit of adventure.</p>', '<p>- Free Internet Access</p><p>- Free Parking</p><p>- Restaurant</p><p>- Fitness Center</p><p>- Pool</p><p>- Spa</p><p>- Digital Key</p><p>- Digital Check-In</p><p>- Resort Property</p><p>- Laundry</p><p>- Concierge</p><p>- Meeting Facilities</p>', '<p>* Complimentary 30-minute camp photo shoot including 1 complimentary e-portrait. Reservation required 24 hours in advance.&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Children Policy :</strong>&nbsp;</p><p>*&nbsp;The river tents and Keliki Valley tents are not suitable for families with infants and children below the age of 10.&nbsp;</p><p>* The child and 1 infant can stay free of charge with the parents using the tent&rsquo;s existing bedding configuration according to maximum bedding capacity stated below, breakfast included.</p><p>*&nbsp;A cot for infants is provided with our compliments.</p><p>*&nbsp;&nbsp;A child is defined as a person between the ages of 4-12 years&rsquo; old, whereas an infant is defined as a person below the age of 4 years&rsquo; old.&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Honeymoon Amenity :&nbsp;</strong></p><p>* Honeymoon cake, one flower bath and one bouquet of flowers await the couple - once during their stay&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Anniversary Amenity :&nbsp;</strong></p><p>* Two Tridatu bracelets and one anniversary cake await the couple - once during the guest&#39;s stay&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Birthday Amenity :&nbsp;</strong></p><p>* One birthday cake and a special surprise await the guset - once during the guest&#39;s stay&nbsp;</p>', 'Active', '1669619519_Capella Ubud.jpg', 14, 'https://capellahotels.com/en/capella-ubud', 'https://g.page/CapellaUbud?share', NULL, NULL, '<p><strong>Low Season :&nbsp;</strong></p><p>15 Days prior to the arrival : No charge&nbsp;</p><p>14 &amp; 8 Days prior to the arrival : 1 Night&#39;s room charge&nbsp;</p><p>7 Days prior to the arrival date on the arrival date : 100% Total booking&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Shoulder Season :&nbsp;</strong></p><p>22 Days prior to the arrival : No charge&nbsp;</p><p>21 &amp; 15 Days prior to the arrival : 1 Night&#39;s room charge&nbsp;</p><p>14 Days prior to the arrival : 100% Total booking&nbsp;</p><p><strong>High/Peak Season :&nbsp;</strong></p><p>46 Days prior to the arrival : No charge&nbsp;</p><p>45 &amp; 31 Days prior to the arrival : 1 Night&#39;s room charge&nbsp;</p><p>30 Days prior to the arrival : 100% Total booking&nbsp;</p><p><strong>No Show :&nbsp;</strong></p><p>Any no-show on a pre-booked reservation will be subject to a no-show penalty equalling a full stay. Subsequent nights will be released for resale.&nbsp;</p>', NULL, '2022-11-26 20:12:00', '2023-06-16 10:33:19');
