(56, 'Kappa Senses Ubud', 'Ou4g8w4yeMzlCP27UtutEO5uOr', 'Ubud', 'Banjar Tanggayuda, Jalan Taman Sari, Kedewatan, Ubud, Gianyar Bali 80571, Indonesia', 'Santi Triana', '03612013888', '<p>At Kappa Senses Ubud, experience divine moments in the land of the gods, in an upscale, environmentally and socially responsible setting. Travel to one of the most coveted islands of the planet and immerse yourself amidst verdant rice fields, whose charm and beauty unfailingly astonish you. Dive into the romantic and passionate world of Rama and Shinta, the Balinese Romeo and Juliet. Whether you are looking for a place to reclaim your inner peace, or a hideaway haven in the midst of a lush jungle, come with an open heart and return forever changed by this enchanting destination and meaningful experiences.</p>', '<p>&bull; Daily Kappa Senses&rsquo; instant as per resort&rsquo;s schedule<br />&bull; Shuttle service to a designated area in Ubud town based on the resort&rsquo;s schedule<br />&bull; Wi-Fi in rooms and throughout the resort<br />&bull; Use of the gym and two resort&rsquo;s swimming pool</p>', '<p>*Daily breakfast</p><p>*A minimum of three (3) nights stay is required for period from 21st December 2023 to 8th January 2024</p><p>*There is compulsory gala dinner on New Year&#39;s eve - 31st December 2023&nbsp;</p><p>*Departure on 31st December 2023 is not permitted</p><p>*Check out on 31st December 2023 is not permitted.</p><p>*Check-in and check-out is not permitted on Balinese silent day &ndash; Nyepi: between 6:00am on 11th March 2024 and 6:00am on 12th March 2024.</p><p><strong>Honeymoon Amenities :&nbsp;</strong></p><p>*A box of home-made treats&nbsp;</p><p>*Honeymoon decoration in the room upon arrival&nbsp;</p><p>*Honeymoon amenities are valid throughout the contracting period and are combinable with all rates and promotions. Proof of marriage within 6 months must be presented at the time of booking.&nbsp;</p>', 'Active', '1669623019_kappasensesubud.jpg', 14, 'https://www.kappasenses.com', 'https://goo.gl/maps/rdKiL45N5Rcyoin2A', NULL, NULL, '<p>*Cancellation must be received in writing by the Resort or its representative and confirmed by the Resort as received&nbsp;</p><p>*Late arrivals, no show and early departures will be charged in full without any exception</p><p><strong>Season 1 :&nbsp;</strong></p><p>*Bookings cancelled between 14 days and 8 days prior to arrival date will incur cancellation charges equal to one night accomodation&nbsp;</p><p>*Bookings cancelled within 7 days of the date of arrival date will incur cancellation charges equal to 100% of the total booking&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Season 2 and 3 :&nbsp;</strong></p><p>*Bookings cancelled between 45 days and 31 days prior to arrival date will incur cancellation charges equal to one night accomodation</p><p>*Bookings cancelled within 30 days of the date of arrival will incur cancellation charges equal to 100% of the total booking</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, '2022-11-26 21:10:19', '2023-06-26 07:44:47'),
(57, 'Komaneka Tanggayuda', 'ocGzcbYCyCQgpPjaPfpK7dhnoD', 'Ubud', 'Br. Tanggayuda, Kedewatan, Kecamatan Ubud, Kabupaten Gianyar, Bali 80571', 'Agus Pramana', '03610978123', '<p>Komaneka at Tanggayuda, established in 2001, is a quiet resort of almost 2 hectares, beautifully situated amidst tropical forest at the edge of a neighboring village, with views to the sacred volcano, Mount Batukaru, and the Oos River. At a slightly higher elevation than Ubud, the air is fresh and invigorating.</p>', '<p>- Free Internet Access</p><p>- Free Parking</p><p>- Restaurant</p><p>- Fitness Center</p><p>- Pool</p><p>- Spa</p><p>- Digital Key</p><p>- Digital Check-In</p><p>- Resort Property</p><p>- Laundry</p><p>- Concierge</p><p>- Meeting Facilities&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>', '<ul><li>Daily breakfast</li><li>Daily afternoon tea with Balinese and Western cakes</li></ul>', 'Draft', '1669689387_Komaneka Tanggayuda.jpg', 5, 'https://tanggayuda.komaneka.com/', 'https://goo.gl/maps/3RFD6Bi1bCnRs4Kf9', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-11-27 15:36:27', '2022-11-27 15:36:27'),
(58, 'Komaneka Bisma', 'DiVFq9W5lqwbM7BFTPmBorZGVK', 'Ubud', 'Jl. Bisma, Ubud, Kecamatan Ubud, Kabupaten Gianyar, Bali 80571', 'Bagus Pramana', '0361971933', '<p>This five-hectare resort built in 2008 was the first luxury boutique resort in the up-and-coming area on Bisma Lane near the center of Ubud. Set on a slope overlooking the Campuhan river valley, the suites and villas have splendid views of a tropical forest valley and the resort&#39;s own rice fields. A sophisticated Ubud getaway near the center of town.</p>', '<p>- Free Internet Access</p><p>- Free Parking</p><p>- Restaurant</p><p>- Fitness Center</p><p>- Pool</p><p>- Spa</p><p>- Digital Key</p><p>- Digital Check-In</p><p>- Resort Property</p><p>- Laundry</p><p>- Concierge</p><p>- Meeting Facilities&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>', '<ul><li>Daily breakfast</li><li>Daily afternoon tea with Balinese and Western cakes</li></ul>', 'Draft', '1669690456_Komaneka Bisma.jpg', 5, 'https://www.komaneka.com/bisma', 'https://goo.gl/maps/yz7DMScZmasSxwTp9', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-11-27 15:54:16', '2022-11-27 15:54:16'),
(59, 'Komaneka Rasa Sayang', 'D9oW7gwgp5F23a2nT6Xwzd8HkR', 'Ubud', 'Jl. Monkey Forest, Ubud, Kecamatan Ubud, Kabupaten Gianyar, Bali 80571', 'Bagus Pramana', '0361975491', '<p>Unveiled in 2011, this stylish urban-style hotel is nestled in an oasis on the Monkey Forest road, with immediate access to cultural and lifestyle activities in the center of Ubud. The architecture of this urban-style hotel is modern and stylish, with an extensive use of wood, and interiors furnished with fine Indonesian art.</p>', '<p>- Free Internet Access</p><p>- Free Parking</p><p>- Restaurant</p><p>- Fitness Center</p><p>- Pool</p><p>- Spa</p><p>- Digital Key</p><p>- Digital Check-In</p><p>- Resort Property</p><p>- Laundry</p><p>- Concierge</p><p>- Meeting Facilities</p>', '<ul><li>Daily breakfast</li><li>Daily afternoon tea with Balinese and Western cakes</li></ul>', 'Draft', '1669692677_Komaneka Rasa sayang.jpg', 5, 'https://www.komaneka.com/rasasayang', 'https://g.page/komanekaatrasasayang?share', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-11-27 16:31:19', '2022-11-27 16:37:14'),
(60, 'Rimba Jimbaran Bali by Ayana', '8CSSf1bYLXfs0WNr9iio1hBTEB', 'Jimbaran', 'Sejahtera, Jl. Karang Mas, Jimbaran, South Kuta, Badung Regency, Bali 80364', 'Noriko Takano', '03618468468', '<p>Experience the legendary beauty of Bali in RIMBA&#39;s lush and natural forest setting. Offering a safe and protected family resort destination within the private, 90-hectare AYANA wellness retreat, authentic and contemporary Balinese activities can be explored along Jimbaran Bay without having to leave the property.</p>', '<p>- Free Internet Access</p><p>- Free Parking</p><p>- Restaurant</p><p>- Fitness Center</p><p>- Pool</p><p>- Spa</p><p>- Digital Key</p><p>- Digital Check-In</p><p>- Resort Property</p><p>- Laundry</p><p>- Concierge</p><p>- Meeting Facilities&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>', '<p>* Daily breakfast</p><p>* Rates are applicable for reservation with minimum of two (2) nights stay</p><p>* Christmas and New Year&rsquo;s Eve Dinner is not compulsory &nbsp;</p><p>* Minimum length of stay is three (3) nights for only check in on 30 and 31 December</p>', 'Active', '1669693995_Rimba Looby.avif', 2, 'https://www.ayana.com/bali/rimba-jimbaran', 'https://goo.gl/maps/Fe3xRRUgiWMCxqXeA', NULL, NULL, '<p><strong>Regular Season&nbsp;</strong></p><p>Cancellation within 07 days prior to arrival : 1 night charge&nbsp;</p><p><strong>High Season&nbsp;</strong></p><p>Cancellation within 14 days prior to arrival : 1 night charge&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Peak Season&nbsp;</strong></p><p>Cancellation within 30 days prior to arrival : 100% charge&nbsp;</p><p><strong>No Show&nbsp;</strong></p><p>* A reservation is considered &ldquo;no show&rdquo; if arrival does not occur on the date reserved and the Hotel is not notified of any emergency delays in writing. No show will be subject to a penalty equal to &ldquo;a full charge on whole period of stay&rdquo; (including all the additional arrangement).</p><p>* No show must be paid without reliance on billed vouchers since the clients did not arrive in the hotel, no voucher will be submitted.</p>', NULL, '2022-11-27 16:53:15', '2023-05-31 03:58:15'),
(61, 'Mandapa Ritz Carlton', 'jk3gc6tnjIRT2ZBYpyaK5mzrX1', 'Ubud', 'Jl. Raya Kedewatan, Banjar, Kedewatan, Kecamatan Ubud, Kabupaten Gianyar, Bali 80571', 'Arik Mahardika', '03614792777', '<p>Befitting its name, which means &quot;temple&quot; in Sanskrit, Mandapa, a Ritz-Carlton Reserve offers hotel guests a &ldquo;temple&rdquo; to call their own, a luxury sanctuary for inner discovery and serenity. Nestled within Bali&#39;s cultural heart of Ubud, with the Ayung River floating peacefully alongside, the hotel offers butler-serviced villas and suites; vintage VW convertible tours of villages, rice fields and temples; and dining including the signature Kubu, featuring Mediterranean-European cuisine and private cocoons</p>', '<p>- Free Internet Access<br />- Free Parking<br />- Restaurant<br />- Fitness Center<br />- Pool<br />- Spa<br />- Digital Key<br />- Digital Check-In<br />- Resort Property<br />- Laundry<br />- Concierge<br />- Meeting Facilities</p>', '<ul><li>Daily Breakfast served at Sawah Terrace restaurant for 2 persons, 4 persons for 2 Bedroom Villa and 6 persons for 3 Bedroom Villa&nbsp;</li><li>Minimum 2 nights stay is required during High Season Period</li><li>arrival and departure are not allowed during Nyepi Days on the period of 22 March 2023 and 11 March 2024.</li></ul><p><strong>HONEYMOON SPECIAL OFFER (PROMO CODE: HNM) -&nbsp;Min 3 nights for Suite category. Min 2 nights for Villa category&nbsp;</strong></p><ul><li>Flower bath &amp; bed turndown&nbsp;</li><li>Celebration miniature honeymoon / anniversary cake on arrival&nbsp;</li><li>Couple&#39;s massage for two of 60 minutes Mepijet / Aromatherapy massage&nbsp;</li></ul><p><strong>DINING SPECIAL OFFER (PROMO CODE: DNO) -&nbsp;Min 3 nights for Suite category. Min 2 nights for Villa category&nbsp;</strong></p><ul><li>One-time three-course menu Dinner at Sawah Terrace restaurant for two persons&nbsp;</li><li>One-time Afternoon Tea [Mandapa Dulang] at The Library for two persons&nbsp;</li><li>Dinner benefit not applicable during Christmas, New Year, Chinese New Year and Easter day&nbsp;</li></ul>', 'Active', '1669695540_Mandapa.jpg', 14, 'https://www.ritzcarlton.com/en/hotels/indonesia/mandapa', 'https://g.page/mandapareserve?share', NULL, NULL, '<p><strong>High Season :&nbsp;</strong></p><ul><li>Cancellation less than 30 days prior to arrival or no show, a cancellation fee equal to entire stay will be levied.&nbsp;</li></ul><p><strong>Shoulder Season :&nbsp;</strong></p><ul><li>Cancellation less than 21 days prior to arrival or no show, a cancellation fee equal to entire stay will be levied.&nbsp;</li></ul><p><strong>&nbsp;Low Season :&nbsp;</strong></p><ul><li>Cancellation less than 14 days prior to arrival or no show, a cancellation fee equal to entire stay will be levied.&nbsp;</li></ul>', NULL, '2022-11-27 17:19:00', '2023-06-26 09:55:44'),
(62, 'Grand Mirage', 'CwspbSvdEQXTzaGzub4vjJnUSE', 'Nusa Dua', 'Jl. Pratama No 74, Tanjung Benoa 80363 Nusa Dua - Bali, Indonesia', 'Ade Ditayanti', '0361771888', '<p>Set on the southern part of Bali, Tanjung Benoa &ndash; Nusa Dua resort area, Grand Mirage Resort and Thalasso Bali spa is blessed with a hypnotizing view of Indian Ocean. This Bali resort is 25 minutes away from Ngurah Rai International Airport. The resort is also within walking distance of numerous shopping outlets, convenience stores and merchandise shops to choose from. With its pristine private beach, this 5 star beachfront Bali resort offers wonderful experiences of spending leisure time in a luxury hotel. With all the luxury inclusions, Grand Mirage Resort and Thalasso Bali Spa is definitely worth listing on every Bali itinerary!</p>', '<p>&bull; Beach Volley Ball<br />&bull; Main Swimming Pool<br />&bull; Pool at Family Paradise<br />&bull; Infinity Pool (Adult Only)<br />&bull; Motorized Water Sport<br />&bull; Non-Motorized Water Sport<br />&bull; Sea Walker<br />&bull; Fitness Center<br />&bull; Games Lounge<br />&bull; Yoga Class<br />&bull; Bicycle Tour Rental<br />&bull; Table Tennis<br />&bull; Mahjong Room<br />&bull; Karaoke Room<br />&bull; Cooking Demo</p>', '<ul><li>Daily breakfast</li><li>No check in and check out on 31 December 2022 &amp; 01 January 2023&nbsp;</li><li>Minimum 3 nights stay during Peak Season Period (24 Dec 22 -&nbsp; 4 Jan 23)</li></ul>', 'Draft', '1669707651_Grand Mirage.jpg', 5, 'https://www.grandmirage.com/', 'https://goo.gl/maps/LAcvHEKqXuhr1muk6', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-11-27 20:40:51', '2022-11-27 20:40:51'),
(63, 'Samabe Bali Suite and Villa', 'Mvh6lI939Fvlrm309BuMgycSN7', 'Nusa Dua', 'Barong - Barong Sawangan, Jl. Pura, Jl. Raya Nusa Dua Selatan, Benoa, Kec. Kuta Sel., Kabupaten Badung, Bali 80363', 'Ade Ditayanti', '03618468633', '<p>Situated in the secluded part of Bali, Nusa Dua, Samabe Bali Suites &amp;amp; Villas epitomises the tranquility of a beach resort in a lavish style. The Bali luxury resort sits on 8 hectare land with 81 suites &amp;amp; villas,&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; 2 restaurants, and 2 bars.</p>', '<p>- Infinity Pool<br />- Free Internet Access<br />- Free Parking<br />- Restaurant<br />- Fitness Center<br />- Pool<br />- Spa<br />- Digital Key<br />- Digital Check-In<br />- Resort Property<br />- Laundry<br />- Concierge<br />- Meeting Facilities</p>', '<ul><li>Daily buffet breakfast in Rempah-rempah Restaurant or in your own private suites or villas</li><li>Daily free-flow non alcoholic beverages at any of the open restaurants and bars</li><li>Complimentary one time daily replenished mini bar, stocked with beer and soft drinks</li><li>Daily afternoon tea served in beach cave starting from 14.30 to 17.00 hours</li></ul>', 'Draft', '1669709166_samabe.jpg', 5, 'https://www.samabe.com/', 'https://goo.gl/maps/s9Tb3R46Tmi5LEMQ8', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-11-27 21:06:06', '2022-11-27 21:06:06'),
(64, 'Maya Ubud Resort and Spa', 'miXOTaXeYCNcVFEzjNBQtZB6Bl', 'Ubud', 'Jl. Gn. Sari, Peliatan, Kecamatan Ubud, Kabupaten Gianyar, Bali 80571', 'Mr. Wilaca', '0361977888', '<p>Deep inside Bali&#39;s cultural heart, and somewhere outside of linear time, Maya Ubud Resort &amp; Spa unfolds gently across 10-hectares of lush tropical landscape. The land&#39;s palm tree-fringed contours form a ceremonial walkway that reveals the hidden river valley below.</p>', '<p>- Free Internet Access<br />- Free Parking<br />- Restaurant<br />- Fitness Center<br />- Pool<br />- Spa<br />- Digital Key<br />- Digital Check-In<br />- Resort Property<br />- Laundry<br />- Concierge<br />- Meeting Facilities<br />- Infinity Forest Pool<br />- Kids Pool<br />- Infinity Riverside Pool<br />- The Lounge<br />- Tennis Court<br />- The Gallery<br />- The Lounge</p>', '<ul><li>Daily breakfast</li><li>Afternoon tea in Bar Bedulu.</li><li>Minimum 2 nights stay is required on December 22, 2022 &ndash; January 02, 2023</li><li>No check-out is allowed on December 31, 2022</li><li>There are no compulsory meal plans during the high season periods or during the year-end festive season</li></ul>', 'Draft', '1669710030_Maya Ubud.webp', 5, 'https://www.mayaresorts.com/ubud', 'https://g.page/mayaubud?share', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-11-27 21:20:30', '2022-11-27 21:20:30'),
(65, 'Padma Resort Ubud', 'VHaV7jbQN2QT7fmI01A823DnSC', 'Ubud', 'Padma Resort Ubud Banjar Carik, Desa, Puhu, Kec. Payangan, Kabupaten Gianyar	,Bali, Indonesia', 'Yuliaty Lawandra', '0361752111', '<p>Nestled within an unspoiled river valley and overlooking the enchanting forests of Payangan, the 149-room Padma Resort Ubud is an expansive and tranquil luxury destination. Located north of Ubud, Bali&rsquo;s celebrated capital of arts and culture, Padma Resort Ubud features all the five-star amenities and facilities one would expect from the renowned Padma hospitality brand, including stunning views from every room or suite, a first-class spa, an awe-inspiring 89-metre infinity swimming pool with panoramic views, signature world-class dining and modern event venues. Our Ubud resort is idyllic and the perfect place to refresh your mind and body, and to explore the wonders of north and central Bali.</p>', '<p>- Swimming Pools<br />- The Spa<br />- Wellness<br />- Wolly Kids Club &amp; Games Centre<br />- Sarasvati Concept Store<br />- Guest Services<br />- Transportation<br />- Resort Facilities Map</p>', '<p>* Daily International Breakfast</p><p>* Free use Kids Club &amp; Games Centre* * Kids Club for children aged 4 - 12 years old * Game Centre for children aged 8 - 12 years old</p><p>* No Compulsory Dinner on Christmas and New Year Eve</p><p>* No check-out on 31 December 2022</p><p>* NO check-in/out on Nyepi Day on 2023</p>', 'Active', '1685340945_cover.jpg', 2, 'https://www.padmaresortubud.com/', 'https://g.page/padmaresortubud?share', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-11-27 21:35:47', '2023-05-31 03:48:47'),
(66, 'Plataran Ubud Hotel & Spa', 'yyu41OmIEbvCPZiZ9MJOaDkqXu', 'Ubud', 'Jl. Raya Hanoman Pengosekan, Ubud, Kec. Gianyar, Kabupaten Gianyar ,Bali, Indonesia', 'Wahyu Dwi', '0361978340', '<p>Plataran Ubud Hotel &amp; Spa is a sprawling haven of lush greenery and tranquility located right in the center of Ubud at Jalan Hanoman. With the hustle and bustle amidst the rich cultural immersion in Ubud, Plataran Ubud guests are in for a sweet surprise as they enter and explore the property &ndash; as it is surrounded by beautifully manicured gardens overlooking a stunning panorama of verdant paddy fields, refreshing pool, and a sacred temple that is aged more than 100 years old. Within this lush oasis resides a collection of 51 stylish rooms, suites, villas, and private residence with options to suit all travelers, complemented by an exceptional range of facilities &ndash; among others are beautifully designed infinity pools, spa, semi outdoor gym, meeting venues, convention center, yoga deck, as well as restaurants offering gourmet Balinese, Indonesian, and Western cuisine. Whether seeking a romantic couple&rsquo;s retreat, a memorable family holiday, a refreshing getaway with friends and colleagues, or even a rejuvenating solo travel, this hidden gem is the perfect place to immerse in the cultural base of Bali, offering serenity beyond compare in the heart of the city.</p>', '<p>- Free Internet Access<br />- Free Parking<br />- Restaurant<br />- Pool<br />- Spa<br />- Digital Key<br />- Digital Check-In<br />- Resort Property<br />- Laundry<br />- Concierge<br />- Meeting Facilities&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>', '<ul><li>Daily breakfast</li><li>Daily afternoon tea</li><li>No check out allowed during the date of 31st December of the ongoing year and 1st January of the following year</li></ul>', 'Draft', '1669772940_Plataran Ubud.jpg', 5, 'https://www.plataran.com/plataran-ubud/', 'https://goo.gl/maps/3a52mXk4udzuwLSB6', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-11-28 14:49:01', '2022-11-28 14:49:01'),
(67, 'Sens Hotel & Spa Ubud', 'HanW6GDMd1k8ptUKpXM3lZcndV', 'Ubud', 'Jl. Sukma Kesuma No.1, Banjar Tebesaya, Kecamatan Ubud, Kabupaten Gianyar	,Bali, Indonesia', 'Chintya Dewi', '03618493328', '<p>The origin of the name SenS is French and has a double meaning. SenS is the name of a commune in the Burgundy region in north-central France, 120 km from Paris. It is crossed by the Rivers Yonne and Vanne. SenS is steeped in history. It has, over time, been an important Roman settlement; the capital of the Senones, a powerful Gallic tribe; and an important religious center and ecclesiastical hub.</p><p>SenS, in the French language, also means sense, way, feeling, direction, consciousness, opinion and meaning.</p>', '<p>- Free Internet Access<br />- Free Parking<br />- Restaurant<br />- Fitness Center<br />- Pool<br />- Spa<br />- Digital Key<br />- Digital Check-In<br />- Resort Property<br />- Laundry<br />- Concierge<br />- Meeting Facilities</p>', '<ul><li>Buffet Breakfast for 2 persons</li><li>No check in/check out allowed on 3 rd March 2022 and 22nd March 2023 (Balinese silent day)</li></ul>', 'Draft', '1669774536_Sens Ubud.jpg', 5, 'https://www.senshotelsresorts.com/', 'https://goo.gl/maps/j3Z3da2Db8RKMo4Z8', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-11-28 15:15:36', '2022-11-28 15:41:42'),
(68, 'Seres Spring Resort & Spa', '82aV1HDcufl5pU6qVSaInVrqxt', 'Ubud', 'Jalan Jukut Paku, Singakerta, Ubud, Singakerta, Kecamatan Ubud, Kabupaten Gianyar	,Bali, Indonesia', 'Chintya Dewi', '03613012222', '<p>Blissfully nestled amidst verdant valleys, rivers, waterfalls, and ensconced by Bali&rsquo;s iconic terraced rice padi fields, SereS Springs Resort &amp; Spa is a sumptuous and sedate five-star getaway that is culturally-inspired by Bali&rsquo;s ritual-rich traditions to deliver an authentic and unique experience beyond compare.<br />Complete with warm hospitality, artisanal artwork and traditional touches throughout the panoramic grounds, SereS Springs Resort &amp; Spa celebrates the rich culture of its island home whilst treating discerning travellers to lavishly-appointed residences, sophisticated amenities, elegant indulgences and a collection of gourmet restaurants that overlook the majestic and holy Mount Agung.</p>', '<p>- Free Internet Access<br />- Free Parking<br />- Restaurant<br />- Fitness Center<br />- Pool<br />- Spa<br />- Digital Key<br />- Digital Check-In<br />- Resort Property<br />- Laundry<br />- Concierge<br />- Meeting Facilities</p>', '<ul><li>Daily Breakfast.</li><li>No check in/check out allowed on 3 rd March 2022 &amp; 22 March 2023 (Balinese silent day)</li></ul>', 'Draft', '1669775948_Seres Ubud.jpg', 5, 'https://www.sereshotelsresorts.com/', 'https://goo.gl/maps/taRxdgjuNCK4jJYLA', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-11-28 15:39:08', '2022-11-28 15:39:08'),
(69, 'Tanah Gajah, a Resort by Hadiprana', 'N7r4CSKmdL7bSJAY46JbJWqvnI', 'Ubud', 'Jalan Goa Gajah, Tengkulak Kaja Ubud, Gianyar, Bali 80571, Indonesia', 'Bima Hartono', '62361975685', '<p>Hidden among the lush undulating hills of Bali&rsquo;s culture-rich highlands, Tanah Gajah, a Resort by Hadiprana (former The Chedi Club Tanah Gajah, Ubud) sits among thriving rice fields as far as the eye can see. Just outside the artists&rsquo; village of Ubud, the former estate of Hendra Hadiprana &ndash; one of Indonesia&rsquo;s most respected art collectors &ndash; has been transformed into an intimate luxury resort with twenty individual villas, each featuring unique and original Balinese artworks from his collection.</p>', '<ul><li>Dining</li><li>Spa</li><li>Wedding &amp; events</li></ul>', '<ul><li>Daily a la carte breakfast</li><li>Daily afternoon tea 16:00 &ndash; 18:00</li><li>Daily sunset cocktails 18:00 &ndash; 19:00</li><li>No check-in and check-out on 31 December 2023 and 1 January 2024. Not required any minimum stay during this period&nbsp;</li></ul><p>Minimum Stay Benefit :&nbsp;</p><ul><li>2 Nights will get 1x complimentary Balinese Massage for two&nbsp;</li><li>3 Nights will get 1x complimentary Balinese Massage for two&nbsp;</li><li>4 Nights will get 3 Nights benefit AND one time picnic lunch&nbsp;</li></ul><p><strong>Honeymoon and Wedding Anniversary :&nbsp;</strong></p><p>Honeymoon guests in any room category, without any minimum stay will receive the following benefits :&nbsp;</p><ul><li>1x Honeymoon Cake on turndown on the night of day of arrival&nbsp;</li><li>1x Special Aromatheraphy floral bath on the first&nbsp;night of the day of arrival&nbsp;</li></ul>', 'Active', '1669776947_Tanah Gajah Resort.jpg', 14, 'https://www.tanahgajahubud.com/en', 'https://goo.gl/maps/nGpUzqZNu1cWRTY17', NULL, NULL, '<p><strong>Regular Season :&nbsp;</strong></p><ul><li>Cancellation fee equivalent to up to 1 night&#39;s room charge will be imposed if cancellation notice is received between 14 - 03 days prior to arrival&nbsp;</li><li>Cancellation fee equivalent to up to full duration of stay room charge will be imposed if cancellation notice is received less than 03 days prior to arrival&nbsp;</li></ul><p><strong>Peak Season :&nbsp;</strong></p><ul><li>Cancellation fee equivalent to 01 night&#39;s room charge will be imposed if cancellation notice is received between 31 days to 21 days to arrival&nbsp;</li><li>Cancellation fee equivalent to the full duration of stay room charges will be imposed if cancellation notice is received less than 21 days prior to arrival&nbsp;</li></ul><p><strong>No Show Policy :&nbsp;</strong></p><ul><li>Any no-show on a pree booked reservation will be subject to a no-show penalty equivalent to full duration of stay&nbsp;</li></ul>', NULL, '2022-11-28 15:55:47', '2023-06-27 06:33:27'),
(70, 'The Garcia Ubud', '7v3tg0BHFEPJLdIMS3ZqEhQWbp', 'Ubud', 'Jl. Raya Silungan, Lodtunduh, Kecamatan Ubud, Kabupaten Gianyar, Bali 80571', 'Dewi Arya', '03612013779', '<p>Encircled by lush rice fields and tropical greenery, The Garcia Ubud is a five-star boutique resort with modern luxury and a touch of contemporary elegance where you&rsquo;ll be swept into a realm of island-inspired sophistication. Stay in style with a collection of well-appointed guestrooms and private pool villas supported by high-end facilities. As a true celebration of Bali&rsquo;s heritage with a unique modern twist, this lifestyle resort is where you will encounter nothing less than pure perfection. Experience gracious hospitality that is second to none as all your needs are met with warm words and a genuine smile. Located in the charming village of Lontunduh, you are just minutes from the cultural attractions, shopping and dining options of central Ubud.</p>', '<p>&bull; Ksuna Restaurant<br />&bull; Camellie Restaurant<br />&bull; In-Room Dining<br />&bull; Kids Centre<br />&bull; Meeting Room<br />&bull; Swimming Pool<br />&bull; Gym<br />&bull; Yoga Centre<br />&bull; Alma Spa &amp; Wellness<br />&bull; Gift Shop<br />&bull; Shuttle Service<br />&bull; Wi-Fi Internet Access<br />&bull; Transport Service<br />&bull; Wedding Destination<br />&bull; MICE &amp; Event<br />&bull; Permaculture Activities<br />&bull; Signature Activities</p>', '<p>Daily breakfast</p>', 'Draft', '1669778984_The Garcia Ubud.jpg', 5, 'http://www.thegarciaubud.com', 'https://goo.gl/maps/CQwWYKS3At6XVzCy5', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-11-28 16:29:44', '2022-11-28 16:29:44'),
(71, 'The Royal Pita Maha', 'lxKSGRgBX5W9XF8Mrr32BTORQm', 'Ubud', 'Kedewatan, Ubud, Gianyar Regency, Bali 80571', 'Mr. Suwetha', '0361980022', '<p>Blessed with uninterrupted views of tropical greenery, The Royal Pita Maha embraces a spiritually charged parcel of landscape in rural Ubud on the island of Bali. This luxury resort has been built with rare sensitivity towards the surrounding environment in an area that descends down to the banks of the Ayung River.<br />Designed to celebrate the traditions, art and culture of Bali, the resort features a collection of private pool villas and supporting facilities overlooking the timeless beauty of the Ayung River. The Royal Pita Maha is a sanctuary for travelers seeking to recharge the body, mind and spirit in the Balinese village of Ubud.</p>', '<p>- Free Internet Access<br />- Free Parking<br />- Restaurant<br />- Fitness Center<br />- Pool<br />- Spa<br />- Digital Key<br />- Digital Check-In<br />- Resort Property<br />- Laundry<br />- Concierge<br />- Meeting Facilities</p>', '<ul><li>Daily breakfast</li><li>Daily afternoon tea with Homemade sweet</li></ul>', 'Draft', '1669779635_Royal Pitamaha.jpg', 5, 'https://www.royalpitamaha-bali.com/', 'https://goo.gl/maps/QkuSX81GXtdgKEPBA', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-11-28 16:40:35', '2022-11-28 16:40:35'),
(72, 'The Sebali Resort', 'eZiCw6aBM1WzlERre2IUtqHeT1', 'Ubud', 'Br. Kepitu, Kecamatan Ubud, Bali 80571', 'I Wayan Yudianta', '0361972233', '<p>The Sebali Resort is an ideal hideaway resort where every pool villa opens up to breathtaking views of the Petanu river valley and surrounding rain forest. You will be escorted crossing the ravine through wooden bridge, marvel at various exotic tropical fruit trees and arrive in front of beautiful traditional Balinese carved door to your own &lsquo;home away from home&rsquo;. Each villa is a luxuriously furnished with spacious bed room, wooden floor, marble bathroom with freestanding bathtub, sunning deck and infinity pool.</p>', '<p>&bull; Spa<br />&bull; Dining<br />&bull; Private pool in each villa</p>', '<ul><li>Daily choice of ala carte Breakfast</li><li>Free daily afternoon tea</li><li>No check out on 31 December (New Year Eve)</li></ul>', 'Draft', '1669789524_Sebali.jpg', 5, 'http://www.thesebali.com/', 'https://goo.gl/maps/SQqo4irvLf1uBmfWA', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-11-28 19:25:24', '2022-11-28 19:25:24'),
(73, 'The Sun of Granary', 'SpCLll1J6bUFh0hlSthc6CMs6b', 'Ubud', 'Banjar Pinjul, Kenderan, Kec. Tegallalang, Kabupaten Gianyar, Bali 80561', 'Arya Wicaya', '03619089028', '<p>The Sun of Granary Resort and Villas presents &ldquo;an escape to paradise&rdquo; in the traditional village of Kenderan, Tegallalang, a part of Ubud region. With locally inspired experiences set against the lush greenery of Tegallalang, the resort takes you closer to the heart and soul of Ubud. Complemented by the surrounding lavish scenery and tranquil ambience, The Sun of Granary Resort and Villas truly lives up to its name. We welcome you on a journey to feel fully connected with nature.</p>', '<p>&bull; Infinity Pool<br />&bull; Kunang Kunang Restautant<br />&bull; Tejas Spa&nbsp;<br />&bull; Yoga lounge<br />&bull; Gym<br />&bull; Kids pool &amp; playground</p>', '<ul><li>Daily breakfast</li><li>No Check In and Check Out on &ndash; seclusion day (Nyepi Day)</li><li>Minimum 2 Nights stay is applicable for check in during period 24,25, 30,31 December</li></ul>', 'Draft', '1669790598_Sun of Granary.jpg', 5, 'https://thesunheaven.com/', 'https://goo.gl/maps/kDAumDjLrzz3cBMX7', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-11-28 19:43:18', '2022-11-28 19:43:18'),
(74, 'Titik Dua Ubud', 'IUPREDOVxpu8syD5maVij3bVOo', 'Ubud', 'Jl. Cok Rai Pudak No.48, Peliatan, Kecamatan Ubud, Kabupaten Gianyar ,Bali, Indonesia', 'Prabowo Tuwiryono', '081139603939', '<p>An independent boutique hotel showcasing contemporary Indonesian design, art, and culture. Located in Peliatan Village, a short 10-min drive from Ubud, Titik Dua features 22 custom-designed rooms, a roof-top restaurant with forest views serving Modern Asian fare, and a speakeasy-inspired Coffee and Cocktail Bar. Featuring 6 multi-purpose spaces and an open-air amphitheater, to accommodate unique corporate events, wellness retreats, and intimate weddings. In keeping with the hotel&rsquo;s mission of bringing local creative talent to the global stage, Titik Dua curates a regular lineup of design-led exhibitions, innovative talks and workshops.</p>', '<p>- Free Internet Access<br />- Free Parking<br />- Restaurant<br />- Fitness Center<br />- Pool<br />- Spa<br />- Digital Key<br />- Digital Check-In<br />- Resort Property<br />- Laundry<br />- Concierge<br />- Meeting Facilities&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>', '<ul><li>Daily breakfast</li><li>For the reason of furniture placement and arrangement, we do not recommend to put extra bed in the room</li></ul>', 'Draft', '1669791685_Titik Dua Ubud.jpeg', 5, 'https://titikdua.id/', 'https://goo.gl/maps/gAYnghvq9wM1Qwp47', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-11-28 20:01:25', '2022-11-28 20:01:25'),
(75, 'Handara Golf & Resort', '9demoFtXj6WyR2IFHEcc82T3Vn', 'Singaraja', 'Desa Singaraja-Denpasar Pancasari Sukasada, Pancasari, Kec. Buleleng, Kabupaten Buleleng	,Bali, Indonesia', 'Anngi Lisandy', '062361771234', '<p>Handara Golf &amp; Resort Bali is a mountain golf course &amp; resort. It boasts a world class golf course in a magnificent setting, cozy hotel and cottage accommodation and a beautiful dining experience.<br />Come and experience the natural wonderland featuring lush tropical gardens, cool weather, and breathtaking mountain scenery. A perfect place to getaway from the hustle and bustle.<br />Handara has benefited from some major recent renovations. Come and experience the new Breeze Terrace with amazing 180 degree panorama over the spectacular mountain view. Another unforgettable experience is the new Soyokaze restaurant where guests can enjoy Japanese cuisine by Handara&rsquo;s veteran chef whilst appreciating the serene ambiance provided by the stunning panorama. Other renovations include the new Pro-Shop, Ladies Locker Room, renovated Cottage and Chalet rooms.</p>', '<ul><li>Golf Lessons</li><li>Caldera Valley Tennis Court</li><li>Pro Shop</li><li>Driving Range</li><li>&nbsp;Locker Rooms</li><li>Golf Club Rental</li><li>Massage Treatments</li><li>&nbsp;Private Outdoor BB</li></ul>', '<ul><li>Daily breakfast</li><li>There might be a meal charge added to bookings made on December 24th Christmas Eve Dinner, Christmas Day Brunch on the 25th and New Year&rsquo;s Eve Dinner on the 31st.</li></ul>', 'Draft', '1669793499_Handara Resort.jpg', 5, 'https://www.handaragolfresort.com/', 'https://goo.gl/maps/7SUnHcdZLFrrVSg17', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-11-28 20:31:39', '2022-11-28 20:31:39'),
(76, 'Munduk Moding Plantation Nature Resort & Spa', 'mcPsOPOBBvGQPLFrJ0Ivmd4g2n', 'Buleleng', 'Jl. Asah Gobleg, Gobleg, Kec. Banjar, Kabupaten Buleleng ,Bali, Indonesia', 'Gede Suparwata', '08113810123', '<p>Munduk Moding Plantation (MMP) is where Bali&rsquo;s skies blend with the water of our infinity pool, the Bali Sea and the towering volcanoes in Java. Where nature creates art. Incomparable views serenaded by birdsong and a choir of crickets. A hideaway nestled in a working coffee plantation surrounded by jungle. Here the real Bali is alive. MMP has been named the best Luxury Eco/Green Hotel in South Asia in 2020 by the World Luxury Hotels Association and our main pool was nominated by Asia Spa as one of the best 10 Infinity pools in the world in 2014.</p>', '<p>- Free Internet Access<br />- Free Parking<br />- Restaurant<br />- Pool<br />- Spa<br />- Digital Key<br />- Digital Check-In<br />- Resort Property<br />- Laundry<br />- Concierge</p>', '<ul><li>Daily breakfast</li><li>Complimentary afternoon tea/coffee will be served with home-made cookies</li><li>Stay 1 night, &nbsp;will get 1 time Head &amp; Shoulder <strong>OR</strong>&nbsp;Footh Massage for 30 minutes</li><li>Stay 2 nights, &nbsp;are entitled to the following benefits: 1&nbsp;time Balinese Massage for 1 Hour for up to 2 persons <strong>OR</strong>&nbsp;alternatively 1 Hour Horse Riding <strong>OR</strong>&nbsp;Cycling <strong>OR 1</strong>&nbsp;time Lunch Trekking to nearby bamboo grove and orchids</li></ul>', 'Draft', '1669797234_Munduk Moding.jpeg', 5, 'https://www.mundukmodingplantation.com/', 'https://goo.gl/maps/1UeBasVDvcLEeu858', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-11-28 21:33:54', '2022-11-28 21:33:54'),
(77, 'Ulaman Eco Luxury Resort', 'aAIJh2JfnBGBOoSOy9Qfge5H7e', 'Tabanan', 'Ulaman Road, Buwit, Kediri, Tabanan Regency	,Bali, Indonesia', 'Tiara Ong', '081238580063', '<p>A secluded, lush haven of tranquility awaits you. Spending any amount of time at distinctive Ulaman Eco Retreat will result in you feeling renewed and invigorated while leaving the smallest ecological footprint possible. Recharge your mind, body and soul. Ulaman offers a unique holistic retreat experience&mdash;immersed in traditional Balinese culture&mdash;for people who strive to live more consciously without compromising comfort and luxury.</p>', '<p>- Tennis Court&nbsp;<br />- Waterfall Pool&nbsp;<br />- Infinity Jungle Pool&nbsp;<br />- Free Internet Access<br />- Free Parking<br />- On-Site Restaurant<br />- Fitness Center<br />- Pool<br />- Spa<br />- Digital Key<br />- Digital Check-In<br />- Resort Property<br />- Laundry<br />- Concierge<br />- Meeting Facilities&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>', '<ul><li>Ulaman Eco Luxury Resort in not suitable for children under 12 years old&nbsp;</li><li>Daily Breakfast&nbsp;</li><li>Complimentary 1x&nbsp;refill mini bar (exclude alcoholic)&nbsp;&nbsp;</li><li>Free activities such as morning yoga and meditation (based on resort&#39;s schedule)&nbsp;</li></ul>', 'Active', '1669798273_Ulaman.jpg', 14, 'https://ulamanbali.com/', 'https://goo.gl/maps/dzcKksmUFfGE1qTJA', NULL, NULL, '<p><strong>Low Season :</strong></p><ul><li>Less than 2 rooms : 14 days&nbsp;</li><li>More than 2 rooms : 30 days&nbsp;</li></ul><p><strong>High Season :&nbsp;</strong></p><ul><li>Less than 2 rooms : 21 days&nbsp;</li><li>More than 2 rooms : 30 days&nbsp;</li></ul><p><strong>Peak Season :&nbsp;</strong></p><ul><li>Less than 2 rooms : 60 days&nbsp;</li><li>More than 2 rooms : 90 days</li></ul><p>Cancellation or no-show fee equivalent to the contracted rate for the booked period for each room cancelled or unutilized.&nbsp;</p>', NULL, '2022-11-28 21:51:13', '2023-06-27 08:36:55'),
(78, 'Plataran Menjangan Resort & Spa', 'ml7BpJ6zjI9sBS3Bwt6IvBpnMs', 'Gilimanuk', 'West Bali National Park, Jl. Raya Seririt  Gilimanuk, Gerokgak, Pejarakan, Gerokgak,	,Bali, Indonesia', 'I.B Ketut Panca Wisnawa', '08111556352', '<p>A tranquil hideaway cocooned within the protected sanctuary of West Bali National Park. Plataran Menjangan Resort &amp; Spa offers an escape to nature at its most beautifully raw and untouched. Experience the epitome of luxury, privacy and comfort in the traditional Joglo villas of this unique eco retreat. Being the epicentre of ecotourism, Plataran Menjangan is blessed with 175 floras and 167 faunas (including the world endangered heritage birds &ndash; Bali starling) and its lush greeneries, calming blue ocean and majestic backdrops of mountains and hills surrounding the area.<br />Experience the epitome of luxury, privacy and comfort in the traditional Joglo villas of this unique eco retreat, at one with nature in the midst of the forest or right by the ocean. Dine along the oceanfront on a world of fresh flavours crafted from the treasures of the garden and sea. Listen to the song of the exotic Bali Starling while exploring the beauty of the wild, trekking through the jungle, kayaking through the mangrove canal, diving in crystal clear waters, or enjoying the romance of a sunset cruise.</p>', '<p>- Free Internet Access<br />- Free Parking<br />- On-Site Restaurant<br />- Fitness Center<br />- Pool<br />- Spa<br />- Digital Key<br />- Digital Check-In<br />- Resort Property<br />- Laundry<br />- Concierge<br />- Meeting Facilities&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />- Wantilan<br />- Infinity Swimming Pool<br />- Plataran Private Cruise Jetty<br />- Plataran Water World<br />- Observation Deck<br />- Endemic Tree Planting<br />- Bali Starling Sanctuary</p>', '<ul><li>Daily breakfast</li><li>Daily afternoon tea.</li><li>No check out allowed during the date of 31st December of the ongoing year and 1st January of the following year</li></ul>', 'Draft', '1669863014_Plataran Menjangan.jpg', 5, 'https://www.plataran.com/plataran-menjangan/', 'https://goo.gl/maps/LcVmKj6NW6nenT618', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-11-29 15:50:14', '2022-11-29 15:50:14'),
(79, 'Adiwana Warnakali Resort', 'NjlGiZEtCrfKqE2w4iet1a8ovk', 'Nusa Penida', 'Sakti, Nusa Penida, Klungkung Regency, Bali 80771', 'Mr. Angga', '03616207000', '<p>Perched 20 meters above the tropical beach of Nusa Penida, Adiwana Warnakali is ready to welcome its guest with unparalleled beauty, ultimate relaxation and endless adventure, Explore the legendary underwater beauty of Nusa Penida right from our beachfront. For the diving enthusiast, we have the Warnakali Dive Center that offers PADI courses and Scuba Diving Safari. As it sits on a tall cliff, the hotel was built Following nature&rsquo;s contour. Each room are layered and overlooking the gorgeous ocean as well as its neighboring island of Nusa Ceningan. &nbsp;Enjoy a day by the pool facing the ocean or another option is to spend the day to explore Nusa Penida&rsquo;s finest attractions, such as Angel Billabong, Atuh Beach and many more. Afterward, relax and find your bliss at the famous Tejas Spa.</p>', '<p>- Free Internet Access<br />- Free Parking<br />- Restaurant<br />- Fitness Center<br />- Pool<br />- Spa<br />- Digital Key<br />- Digital Check-In<br />- Resort Property<br />- Laundry<br />- Concierge<br />- Meeting Facilities&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />- Warnakali Dive Center</p>', '<p>- Daily breakfast<br />-&nbsp;Daily afternoon tea<br />-&nbsp;No Check In and Check Out on &ndash; seclusion day (Nyepi Day)<br />-&nbsp;Minimum 2 Nights stay is applicable for check in during period 24,25, 30,31 December</p>', 'Draft', '1669863781_Adiwana Warnakali.jpg', 2, 'https://adiwanahotels.com/warnakali-resort-nusa-penida-bali/', 'https://goo.gl/maps/Gfyx2gBq3gGcztyf9', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-11-29 16:03:01', '2023-04-17 20:22:03'),
(80, 'Adiwana d\'Nusa Beach Club and Resort', '2Oe0PYyeft4eyNYgijtAtZH3HD', 'Nusa Penida', 'Light House Beach, Jl. Jungutbatu, Nusa lembongan, Kec. Nusa Penida, Kabupaten Klungkung, Bali 87500', 'Ayu Sukraeni', '03614720750', '<p>The ultimate luxury retreat for the adventure-seekers, Adiwana d&rsquo;Nusa Beach Club and Resort is ready to reintroduce their newly rebranded property under Adiwana management. Nestled in the Light House Beach of Jungut Batu Village, the resort sits graciously, merely 30 minutes from Sanur Harbor. Encompassing white sand beach and lush mangrove forest, you will soon discover that this resort is what tropical dream holiday is made of.&nbsp;<br />Bask in the warm sun, or explore the exotic island of Nusa Lembongan. Or simply relax in the comfort of our beautifully designed rooms, suites, and villas. To make your stay unforgettable, our resort comes with a spa, restaurants and beach club. Ready for the adventure of a lifetime? Come and have the time of your life at Adiwana d&rsquo;Nusa Beach Club and Resort.</p>', '<p>- Free Internet Access<br />- Free Parking<br />- Restaurant<br />- Fitness Center<br />- Pool<br />- Spa<br />- Digital Key<br />- Digital Check-In<br />- Resort Property<br />- Laundry<br />- Concierge<br />- Meeting Facilities&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />- Beach Club</p>', '<ul><li>Daily breakfast</li><li>Daily afternoon tea</li><li>No Check In and Check Out on &ndash; seclusion day (Nyepi Day)</li><li>Minimum 2 Nights stay is applicable for check in during period 24,25, 30,31 December</li></ul>', 'Draft', '1669864746_Adinawa D\'Nusa.jpg', 5, 'https://adiwanahotels.com/dnusa-resort-nusa-lembongan-bali/', 'https://goo.gl/maps/RwVcXkZc7b8WgNyx8', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-11-29 16:19:06', '2022-11-29 16:19:06'),
(81, 'Samuh Ocean Sunset Hotel by WizZeLa', 'jgsr1qY5IW3izOh1oAmqRGTB2q', 'Nusa Penida', 'Banjar Anyar, Dusun Sebunibus 80771, Nusa Penida', 'Ratna Desi', '7996905', '<p>Hotel with Ocean View in Nusa Penida<br />You can see Ocean View, Sunrise, Sunset, Lembongan</p>', '<p>- Free Internet Access<br />- Free Parking<br />- Restaurant<br />- Fitness Center<br />- Pool<br />- Spa<br />- Digital Key<br />- Digital Check-In<br />- Resort Property<br />- Laundry<br />- Concierge<br />- Meeting Facilities</p>', '<ul><li>Daily breakfast</li><li>Compulsory : New Year&rsquo;s Eve Dinner on 31 December</li><li>Samuh Ocean Sunset Hotel by WizZeLa&nbsp;do not accept children under 12 year old&nbsp;</li></ul>', 'Draft', '1669867871_Samuh Ocean Sunset.webp', 5, 'https://www.wizzela.com', 'https://goo.gl/maps/VHpf6hHqdp5YWZg29', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-11-29 17:11:11', '2022-11-29 17:11:11'),
(82, 'Mua Nusa Penida', 'HZEVyvCkR0AuI4T8dYP4pOKVVg', 'Nusa Penida', 'Sakti, Nusa Penida, Klungkung Regency	,Bali, Indonesia', 'Bagus Indra Saputra', '03616208999', '<p>MAUA Nusa Penida &ndash; Bali est un resort 5 &eacute;toiles, situ&eacute; sur l&rsquo;&icirc;le de Nusa Penida, nich&eacute; au sommet de la colline de Gamat Bay. Trop longtemps m&eacute;connue, Nusa Penida est une destination spectaculaire, facilement accessible depuis Bali. Ce n&rsquo;est que depuis quelques ann&eacute;es qu&rsquo;elle est devenue la destination pris&eacute;e des explorateurs aspirant &agrave; un retour &agrave; la nature.<br />A MAUA Nusa Penida, il sera enfin possible de decouvrir et de profiter de cette destination extraordinaire avec vue sur la colline de Gamat Bay dans un resort international emblematique 5 etoiles tout confort. Celui-ci se trouve &agrave; environ une demi-heure de ferry depuis Sanur et vingt minutes de voiture depuis le terminal des ferries de Nusa Penida.</p>', '<p>- Free Internet Access<br />- Free Parking<br />- Restaurant<br />- Fitness Center<br />- Pool<br />- Spa<br />- Digital Key<br />- Digital Check-In<br />- Resort Property<br />- Laundry<br />- Concierge<br />- Meeting Facilities</p>', '<ul><li>Daily Breakfast</li><li>NO CHECK OUT is allowed on 31 December 2022.</li><li>&ldquo;Silent Ocean ( Nyepi Laut ) on 11 October 2022, Please note that the boat will not be able to cross from and to Nusa Penida.</li><li>Minimum 2 nights stay is required during Peak period.</li><li>Respecting Silence Day (Hari Raya Nyepi) on 22 March 2023, NO CHECK IN or CHECK OUT is allowed.</li></ul>', 'Draft', '1669869170_Maua Nusa Penida.jpg', 5, 'https://mauahotel.com/id/beranda/', 'https://goo.gl/maps/hiRSE2vYmHF8fvZg8', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-11-29 17:32:50', '2022-11-29 17:32:50'),
(83, 'AYANA Komodo Waecicu Beach', 'DZHeJFqDDkY76wsL3uaSoLKTNq', 'Labuan Bajo', 'Pantai Waecicu, Labuan Bajo, Kab, Kabupaten Manggarai Barat, Nusa Tenggara Tim. 86554', 'Noriko Takano', '03852441000', '<p>A perfectly balanced retreat sanctuary welcomes you to the heart of Komodo National Park. Experience and create lasting memories in the lap of luxury with state-of-the-art facilities and services while surrounded by unparalleled natural beauty at the best 5-star hotel in Labuan Bajo, AYANA Komodo.</p>', '<p>- Free Internet Access<br />- Free Parking<br />- Restaurants<br />- Fitness Center<br />- Pool<br />- Spa<br />- Digital Key<br />- Digital Check-In<br />- Resort Property<br />- Laundry<br />- Concierge<br />- Meeting Facilities<br />- Kid&#39;s Pool<br />- Waecicu Beach<br />- Jetty Pool<br />- Infinity Pool</p>', '<ul><li>Daily breakfast</li><li>Christmas and New Year&rsquo;s Eve Dinner is not compulsory</li><li>Minimum length of stay is three (3) nights for only check in on 30 and 31 December</li><li>Rates are applicable for reservation with minimum of two (2) nights stay</li></ul>', 'Draft', '1669870377_Ayana Komodo Resort.jpg', 5, 'https://www.ayana.com/labuan-bajo/komodo/', 'https://goo.gl/maps/inKVcPf9Hc7LkNK2A', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-11-29 17:52:57', '2022-11-29 17:52:57'),
(84, 'Komodo Resort', 'C1vscY2NRJDzYkR20mkNvUfVLe', 'Labuan Bajo', 'Tanjung Pelinta, Pulau Sebayur, Komodo, 86754	 ,Sebayur, Indonesia', 'Susan', '628113966557', '<p>Nestled in a sheltered bay fringed with white sand, the Komodo Dive Resort offers a unique and friendly environment to enjoy some of Indonesia&#39;s best diving. Imagine a dive resort in Indonesia where you are welcomed as family on a paradisiac island in the middle of the Komodo archipelago surrounded by crystal clear waters and pristine reefs.<br />The Komodo region is renowned for being among the top dive sites on earth. Divers, snorkelers and photographers from all around the world come to the Komodo National Park to experience its very rich and unique marine biodiversity. As you peruse our site you&#39;ll understand why Komodo is without equal in noble hospitality and experiences that build new traditions and memories that last a lifetime.</p>', '<p>- Free Internet Access<br />- Free Parking<br />- On-Site Restaurant<br />- Fitness Center<br />- Pool<br />- Spa<br />- Digital Key<br />- Digital Check-In<br />- Resort Property<br />- Laundry<br />- Concierge<br />- Meeting Facilities</p>', '<ul><li>3 Meals/day (breakfast, lunch and dinner).</li><li>The room rates applied for a minimum stay of 3 nights</li></ul>', 'Draft', '1669876809_Komodo Resort.jpg', 5, 'https://www.komodoresort.com/', 'https://goo.gl/maps/WDqPGrwVgATyKhp6A', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-11-29 19:40:09', '2022-11-29 19:40:09'),
(85, 'Loccal Collection Hotel', 'N2A8n2Z2LjwZWvZYjmAIzeyioj', 'Labuan Bajo', 'Labuan Bajo, Komodo, West Manggarai Regency	, East Nusa Tenggara, Indonesia', 'Mr. Yunus', '03852440499', '<p>Built into the cliffs of Labuan Bajo, Local Collection&rsquo;s unique aesthetic fuses local craftsmanship and materials with elegant simplicity and attention to detail.</p>', '<p>- Free Internet Access<br />- Free Parking<br />- Restaurant<br />- Fitness Center<br />- Pool<br />- Spa<br />- Digital Key<br />- Digital Check-In<br />- Resort Property<br />- Laundry<br />- Concierge<br />- Meeting Facilities</p>', '<p>Daily breakfast</p>', 'Draft', '1669877784_Loccal Collection Hotel.jpg', 5, 'https://loccalcollection.com/', 'https://goo.gl/maps/YG4qDBaeWRR4Qo4A9', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-11-29 19:56:24', '2022-11-29 19:56:24');
