(86, 'Plataran Komodo', 'BQfSVrQIR4RmCa66wuVPSVeSTm', 'Labuan Bajo', 'Labuan Bajo, Komodo, West Manggarai Regency	, East Nusa Tenggara, Indonesia', 'I.B Ketut Panca Wisnawa', '081139002121', '<p>Secluded in a quiet cove on Waecicu Beach on the island of Flores, Plataran Komodo Resort &amp; Spa is a true luxury labuan bajo resort in tropical paradise. A luxurious base for indulging in sun-kissed days of relaxation and adventure in one of Indonesia&rsquo;s most beautiful and untouched regions.<br />A million miles away from the daily hustle and bustle, luxuriate in the privacy of intimate yet spacious villa abodes that are a charming blend of luxurious comfort and Javanese style. Dine beside the ocean waves, on the beach, or on the jetty &ndash; all under the Flores sun or beneath a romantic canopy of stars. Explore the amazing marine life in the surrounding waters, or hop aboard one of the Plataran private cruises for unforgettable island-hopping excursions and the chance to see the fabled Komodo dragons up close.</p>', '<p>- Atlantis On The Rock<br />- Plataran Water World<br />- Plataran Sunset Hill<br />- Sea Garden Underwater Park<br />- Free Internet Access<br />- Free Parking<br />- On-Site Restaurant<br />- Fitness Center<br />- Pool<br />- Spa<br />- Digital Key<br />- Digital Check-In<br />- Resort Property<br />- Laundry<br />- Concierge<br />- Meeting Facilities</p>', '<ul><li>Daily breakfast.</li><li>Daily afternoon tea</li><li>No check out allowed during the date of 31st December of the ongoing year and 1st January of the following year</li></ul>', 'Draft', '1669879459_Plataran Komodo.jpg', 5, 'https://www.plataran.com/plataran-komodo/', 'https://goo.gl/maps/ocrTtJ7KSGDdXVwD8', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-11-29 20:24:19', '2022-11-29 20:24:19'),
(87, 'The Seraya Resort Komodo', 'GSf2K7IDuRCdfMk8foSgZB9WXH', 'Labuan Bajo', 'Seraya Kecil, Labuan Bajo, Komodo, West Manggarai Regency, East Nusa Tenggara 86763', 'Deiby SIWY', '087860887881', '<p>The Seraya is located on the north coast of Seraya Kecil island, nine kilometres north of Labuan Bajo, the gateway to Komodo National Park. There are a number of ways to get to Labuan Bajo depending on your itinerary. From the West there are daily flights from Bali, Lombok, Jakarta and Surabaya and from the East there are flights and overland cars from Ende, Maumere, Kupang &amp; Bajawa.</p>', '<p>- Free Internet Access<br />- Free Parking<br />- Restaurant<br />- Fitness Center<br />- Pool<br />- Spa<br />- Digital Key<br />- Digital Check-In<br />- Resort Property<br />- Laundry<br />- Concierge<br />- Meeting Facilities</p>', '<ul><li>Daily breakfast</li><li>Extra bed is not available at&nbsp;Beach&nbsp;Front&nbsp;Bungalow&nbsp;room category</li><li>Minimum length of stay is 2 (two) nights per room</li><li>Closed out on Febuary due weather conditions</li></ul>', 'Draft', '1669880896_The Seraya.jpg', 5, 'https://www.theseraya.com/', 'https://goo.gl/maps/oK3iNw5y9ik9ZSjX9', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-11-29 20:48:16', '2022-11-29 20:48:16'),
(88, 'Lelewatu Resort Sumba', 'luGePy6352cga9KIa6IRc73g6e', 'Sumba', 'Jl. Lelewatu No.168, Hoba Wawi, Wanokaka, Sumba, 87272	,East Nusa Tenggara, Indonesia', 'Ni Luh Putu Budi Udayani', '62361233708', '<p>The perfect luxurious escape amidst unspoiled nature, at Lelewatu Resort Sumba.<br />Beyond the thoughtful design, refined style and understated sophistication, every villa in Lelewatu Resort brings the Sumbanese tradition and culture of island living into the stay experience.<br />Spacious rooms, private pool, butler service. Purely yours to enjoy.<br />Your memories with us are crafted with care, delivered from the heart and made to last.</p>', '<p>- Free Internet Access<br />- Free Parking<br />- On-Site Restaurant<br />- Fitness Center<br />- Pool<br />- Spa<br />- Digital Key<br />- Digital Check-In<br />- Resort Property<br />- Laundry<br />- Concierge<br />- Meeting Facilities</p>', '<ul><li>Daily breakfast</li><li>2 nights minimum length of stay all categories in Low season</li><li>5 nights minimum length of stay all categories in High season</li><li>No check-in and check-out on 31st December 2022, 31st December 2024</li></ul>', 'Draft', '1669882124_Lelewatu Resort Sumba.jpg', 5, 'https://lelewatu.com/', 'https://goo.gl/maps/36zkpN3QW5GAGWwD9', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-11-29 21:08:44', '2022-11-29 21:08:44'),
(89, 'AYANA Villas Bali (The Villas at AYANA Resort Bali)', 'o9fey7AfRFb1dhNBUUrxo7gHY1', 'Jimbaran', 'Jalan Karang Mas Sejahtera, Jimbaran, Bali, Indonesia', 'Noriko Takano', '0361702222', '<p>A private pool villa experience is the pinnacle of honeymooning in Bali. Each of our 78 spacious residences provides an impeccable and welcoming sanctuary for travelers in search of flawless romance, wellness, and fine dining - either at the resort&#39;s award-winning venues or within the comfort of the villa. Timeless Indian Ocean views are maximized along the cliff front, with unmatched sunsets, blossoming gardens, and 24/7 butler service.</p>', '<p>&bull; Golf Putting Course<br />&bull; Ayana Kids Club<br />&bull; Spa<br />&bull; Jogging Trail<br />&bull; Ayana Gym<br />&nbsp;</p>', '<ul><li>Daily breakfast</li><li>Rates are applicable for reservation with minimum of two (2) nights stay</li><li>Christmas and New Year&rsquo;s Eve Dinner is not compulsory</li><li>Minimum length of stay is three (3) nights for only check in on 30 and 31 December</li></ul>', 'Active', '1669883533_AYANA_Villa.webp', 14, 'https://www.ayana.com/bali/the-villas-at-ayana/', 'https://goo.gl/maps/dw6CHam7ALRS49Sb9', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-11-29 21:32:13', '2023-05-29 09:44:53'),
(90, 'Amertha Bali Villas', 'RkyrQ2pYpmNnzgBMc4LGVz1AZY', 'Buleleng', 'Jl. Seririt-Gilimanuk No.Ds, Pemuteran, Kec. Gerokgak, Kabupaten Buleleng	,Bali, Indonesia', 'Agung Ambhara', '082341280231', '<p>Amertha is an evolving partnership founded in community involvement. From the outset, we have consulted with village leaders in Pemuteran and we continue to take direction from their wisdom and insight. Balance is the cornerstone of Bali society, and it is our goal to maintain the balance between nature and our cultural environment. You are invited to help us preserve the balance of this precious paradise.</p>', '<p>- Karang Divers<br />- Beachfront Pool<br />- Coral Bay Beachfront Restaurant, Bar and Grill<br />- Prana Spa<br />- Yoga Shala<br />- Prana Basa Genep<br />- Weddings<br />- Coral Restoration Project</p>', '<p>Daily breakfast</p>', 'Draft', '1670204454_Amertha Villa.jpg', 5, 'https://amerthabalivillas.com/', 'https://goo.gl/maps/4KjjBZBxXayPQZxC9', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-12-03 14:40:54', '2022-12-03 14:40:54'),
(91, 'The Lovina Resort', '9Sknuo3KReX8atjyOskKu79K2r', 'Buleleng', 'Kalibukbuk, Jl. Mas Lovina, Kabupaten Buleleng, Bali 81151', 'Dwi Dharmawijaya', '03623435800', '<p>Nestled on the beach, between the Bedugul mountain range and the Bali sea, this tropical island gem is surrounded by various attractions. Dolphin watching, trekking to waterfalls, hot springs and diving or snorkelling around Menjangan island, home to the best preserved coral reef in Bali. Just two and half hours drive from the hustle and bustle of the busy tourist areas in the south, you will enjoy a relaxing Bali holiday.</p>', '<p>&bull; Heliconia Restaurant<br />&bull; Body tonic spa<br />&bull; Beach dining<br />&nbsp;</p>', '<ul><li>Daily breakfast</li><li>All Villas and Suites are with balcony/terrace and equipped with private open-space bathroom with shower/bathtub. All room types are equipped with Sat-TV, mini or maxi-bar, coffee and tea making facilities, individual air-conditioning, additional ceiling fan, hair dryer, private safe deposit box. The Lovina has the largest average standard rooms in Bali</li></ul>', 'Draft', '1670207214_The Lovina.jpg', 5, 'http://www.thelovinabali.com/en/', 'https://goo.gl/maps/p7TAhhQKSfTo2Dmc9', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-12-03 15:26:54', '2022-12-03 15:26:54'),
(92, 'Sudamala Resort, Komodo, Labuan Bajo', '5lX0cArG3nBNKC0zPf0eBvJ4o7', 'Labuan Bajo', 'Jl. Pantai Pede Km.3, Desa Gorontalo-Labuan Bajo Flores, Manggarai Barat, Nusa Tenggara Timur , Labuan Bajo, Indonesia 86754', 'Kadek Yulandari', '0361288555', '<p>Nestled directly on the white sands of Pede Beach, overlooking the Flores Sea and the enchanting islands of Komodo National Park.<br />All 84 suites and villas are ideal for romance, adventure and relaxation, and showcase stylish interiors inspired by the local Flores culture and contemporary amenities. The Garden Suites feature private balconies surrounded by lush greenery, while the Beachfront and Sea View Suites promise breathtaking views of the Labuan Bajo Strait, and the luxurious Private Pool Villas provide expansive courtyards and inviting outdoor pools.<br />Sudajiva Spa, with its own private swimming pool, promises unrivaled relaxation and serenity. The restaurant, pool bar and function space, all beachfront, have been thoughtfully designed for the ultimate bucket list holiday experience.<br />The PADI-certified Aqura Dive, with its own private jetty and state of the art boats, offers options for experienced divers and beginners alike, and excursions can be arranged to UNESCO World Heritage-listed Komodo National Park as well as to a path less traveled into in-land Flores.</p>', '<p>&bull; Swimming Pool<br />&bull; Beach Front Restaurant<br />&bull; Manta Cafe<br />&bull; Spa<br />&bull; Gym<br />&bull; Aqura Dive Center<br />&bull; Meeting room and function space<br />&bull; Direct beach access</p>', '<ul><li>Daily breakfast</li><li>No check out on 31 December</li><li>Minimum stay of three (3) consecutive nights is required during peak season period on 24 December &ndash; 03 January</li></ul><p>&nbsp;</p>', 'Draft', '1670209115_SUDAMALA-SUITES-VILLAS-KOMODO_.jpg', 5, 'http://sudamalaresorts.com/labuanbajo', 'https://goo.gl/maps/aAAWJ4S4eZ3qJudm9', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-12-03 15:58:35', '2022-12-03 15:58:35'),
(93, 'Sudamala Resort, Seraya', 'iHOv2zeyuwxdEQID1bjorXGf6H', 'Labuan Bajo', 'Pulau Seraya Kecil, Labuan Bajo, Kec. Komodo, Kabupaten Manggarai Barat, Nusa Tenggara Tim.', 'Kadek Yulandari', '0361288555', '<p>An authentic definition of a tropical barefoot luxury at its finest, Sudamala Resort, Seraya offers a glimpse of paradise on earth in its island resort situated on an idyllic Seraya Kecil island &ndash; or Pulau Seraya Kecil in Indonesian &ndash; in Flores, Indonesia.</p><p>A beautifully calm sanctuary, this Sudamala Resort, Seraya offers secluded getaway in a breathtaking setting of a secluded island with the abundance of pristine natural wonders, ringed with translucent white sandy beaches, crystal-clear waters and vibrant underwater life for an ultimate Robinson Crusoe experience. With copious unspoiled nature abundantly available to pamper your every sense; in Sudamala Resort, Seraya, luxury comes in the simplest detail.</p>', '<p>- Free Internet Access<br />- Free Parking<br />- Restaurant<br />- Fitness Center<br />- Pool<br />- Spa<br />- Digital Key<br />- Digital Check-In<br />- Resort Property<br />- Laundry<br />- Concierge<br />- Meeting Facilities</p>', '<p>- Daily breakfast<br />- No check out on 31 December<br />- Minimum stay of three (3) consecutive nights is required during&nbsp;high season period on 01 July &ndash; 31 August and peak season period on 24 December &ndash; 03 January</p>', 'Draft', '1670210203_Sudamala Seraya.jpg', 2, 'https://www.sudamalaresorts.com/seraya/', 'https://goo.gl/maps/CknQv1xm6c9va6XV9', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-12-03 16:16:43', '2023-04-17 20:19:31'),
(94, 'Alaya Resort Ubud', 'GXOIKI1pZo6HT7KQYFQIoOf3fs', 'Ubud', 'Jl. Hanoman, Ubud ,Bali, Indonesia', 'Nila Kresna', '0361972200', '<p>With 106 luxurious rooms, Alaya Resort Ubud is a sanctuary of serenity and sophistication in the culturally charged village of Ubud in the island of Bali. It has been built with rare sensitivity towards the surrounding environment and shares its rice terrace views with a number of the communities&rsquo; local independent cafes and eateries, including the neighbouring Bebek Bengil restaurant and Monkey Forest. As part of Ubud&rsquo;s evolving hospitality scene, the exotic boutique property offers guests a stylish place to stay that reflects Ubud&rsquo;s and Bali&rsquo;s unique artistry. A number Bali&rsquo;s most respected and talented designers have collaborated to create this elegant hotel with a distinct sense of belonging.</p>', '<p>- Romantic dinner<br />- Jamu class dala spa<br />- Bamboo bar<br />- Yoga at bale<br />- Jamu class dala spa</p>', '<p>- Daily breakfast<br />-&nbsp;Daily afternoon tea<br />-&nbsp;Extra bed is not recommended due to space constraint however if guest insist it will be set up in front of the wardrobe area with additional charge<br />-&nbsp;Min 2N Stay : free upgade from Deluxe to Alaya Room OR 1x60Mins Spa | &nbsp;Min 4N Stay : free upgrade from Deluxe to Alaya Room and 1x60Mins Spa<br />-&nbsp;Minimum 2 nights stay is applicable for check in during period on 25 December &ndash; 07 January.</p>', 'Active', '1670379163_Alaya Ubud.jpg', 2, 'http://alayahotels.com/alayaresortubud/', 'https://goo.gl/maps/ES5YnknbWgP6jYsn6', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-12-05 15:12:43', '2023-05-26 04:27:08'),
(95, 'Grand Sovereign Kuta Bali', 'kD1FUXxwZM9wgkNeQGFHX4fbrX', 'Kuta', 'Jl. Raya Tuban, Lingkungan Griya No.2, Tuban, Bali 80361', 'Balifta Susilawati', '03613615555', '<p>Grand Sovereign Kuta Bali is a 4 stars hotel with a premium location that provides a high quality standard of services and facilities. The guestrooms, meeting rooms, restaurant and all facilities are tastefully decorated in an Elegant Balinese Tropical. Strategically located to the famous Ngurah Rai International Airport, Kuta Beach, Seminyak, Sanur and only a short walking distance to the souvenir center makes Grand Sovereign Kuta the perfect place for meeting and leisure.</p>', '<p>&bull; Sky Pool &amp; Bar<br />&bull; Nirvana Bali Spa<br />&bull; Jacuzzi &amp; Sauna<br />&bull; Fitness Center<br />&nbsp;</p>', '<ul><li>Daily breakfast</li><li>No Check In and Check Out on 03 March 2022 - Nyepi Day</li></ul>', 'Draft', '1671180682_Grand Sovereign.jpg', 5, 'https://www.grandsovereign.com/', 'https://goo.gl/maps/MhRVvQzhRaDGTHts9', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-12-14 21:51:22', '2022-12-14 21:51:22'),
(96, 'Alaya Dedaun Kuta', 'MvspVrfeJSYKjT1VFAJ4gwYpx3', 'Kuta', 'Jl. Raya Legian 123B Kuta', 'Ayu Puspita', '0361756276', '<p>Steeped in romance, Alaya Dedaun Kuta brings affordable luxury and understated Indonesian elegance to Bali&rsquo;s favourite beachside playground. Designed to embrace the spirit of a traditional village, the property features a collection of just 12 private villas in a concept attuned to the attributes of outdoor living.</p><p>Each villa is a tropical retreat secluded within a native garden compound featuring a generous sized swimming pool and ample space to unwind. Bedroom suites are styled to evoke a sense of privacy with canopied beds and indulging bathroom facilities. Attentive butler service ensures that all needs are effortlessly taken care of with a warm Balinese smile.</p>', '<p>Private swimming pool set within a tropical garden compound<br />Fully equipped gourmet kitchen<br />Stylish living environment<br />Separate shower and bathtub<br />Signature bathroom amenities<br />Air &ndash; Conditioner<br />IDD Telephone<br />Cable TV ( International and local&nbsp; channels)<br />Surround sound home entertainment system<br />Espresso coffee and tea making facilities<br />Minibar<br />Safety deposit box<br />Slippers &amp; Kimonos<br />Hair Dryer<br />Iron ( on request )<br />Baby cot on request<br />Turn down service<br />Laundry, dry cleaning and pressing service</p>', '<p><strong>HONEYMOONERS BENEFITS MINIMUM 2 NIGHTS STAY:</strong><br />- All honeymooners receive upon arrival on complimentary:<br />- Honeymoon decoration on the bed and bath tub<br />- Honeymoon cake<br /><strong>Standard Benefits (2 persons per bedroom):</strong><br />- Complimentary welcome drink, welcome fruit basket, 1 x afternoon tea per stay, daily breakfast, daily<br />- Set up mineral water and omplimentary daily guest activities based on hotel schedule.</p>', 'Active', '1679988410_Alaya Dedaun kuta.webp', 2, 'www.alayahotels.com', 'https://goo.gl/maps/HrWNm7AMdSW7V54k7', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-03-27 17:26:50', '2023-03-28 20:01:48'),
(98, 'AYANA Segara Bali', 'POqhnrskzHD3l6CiUxOgHIGyMn', 'Jimbaran', 'Jimbaran, Kec Kuta Selatan, Kabupaten Badung, Bali.', 'Noriko Takano', '0361702222', '<p>Experience unbeatable sunset views at Segara&rsquo;s rooftop bar or at the largest indoor-outdoor pool in Bali. Located adjacent to AYANA Resort, this new hotel is a quick tram ride away from AYANA&rsquo;s renowned, one-of-a-kind facilities.<br />Each of the rooms and suites offer indoor-outdoor spaces with private terraces and large nature framing windows that welcome in the sweet smell of lush tropical trees and the cool breeze of the Indian Ocean. Designed to allow for sweeping nature views at every moment, the rooms&#39; clean modern lines are accented with rich materials that celebrate the local region.</p>', '<p>* Golf Putting Course&nbsp;</p><p>* Jogging Trail&nbsp;</p><p>* Monkey Forest&nbsp;</p><p>* Spa</p><p>* Bussines Center&nbsp;</p><p>* AYANA Kids Club&nbsp;</p><p>* AYANA Gym&nbsp;</p>', '<p>* Daily Breakfast&nbsp;</p><p>* Rates are applicable for reservation with minimum of two (2) nights stay</p><p>* Christmas and New Year&rsquo;s Eve Dinner is not compulsory</p><p>* Minimum length of stay is three (3) nights for only check in on 30 and 31 December&nbsp;</p>', 'Active', '1685327020_AYANA Segara Bali Main Pool and Exterior View Resized.jpg', 2, 'https://www.ayana.com/bali/ayana-segara/', 'https://goo.gl/maps/jWb5D1kYUX1cXwzp7', NULL, NULL, '<p><strong>Regular Season</strong></p><p>Cancellation 7 days prior to arrival 1 night charge&nbsp;</p><p><strong>High Season&nbsp;</strong></p><p>Cancellation 14 days prior to arrival 1 night charge&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Peak Season&nbsp;</strong></p><p>Cancellation 30 days prior to arrival full charge&nbsp;</p><p><strong>No Show&nbsp;</strong></p><p>* A reservation is considered &ldquo;no show&rdquo; if arrival does not occur on the date reserved and the Hotel is not notified of any emergency delays in writing. No show will be subject to a penalty equal to &ldquo;a full charge on whole period of stay&rdquo; (including all the additional arrangement).</p><p>* No show must be paid without reliance on billed vouchers since the clients did not arrive in the hotel, no voucher will be submitted.&nbsp;</p>', NULL, '2023-05-29 02:23:40', '2023-06-05 02:02:36'),
(99, 'Ibis Styles Hotel', 'TB8Da37WviIysV6yHNuzLxndLM', 'Nusa Dua', 'Jl. Pratama 57A, Tanjung Benoa, Nusa Dua, Bali', 'Widya Kumala', '03618647788', '<p>Offering an outdoor swimming pool, Ibis Styles Bali Benoa is a hotel located a 5-minute drive away from the Bali Collection shopping area. The hotel features 2 dining options, a gym, and modern rooms with en-suite bathrooms. Free Wi-Fi is accessible throughout the property.</p><p>The air-conditioned rooms at Ibis Styles Bali Benoa showcase a cheerful interior with vibrant colors. All rooms are equipped with a flat-screen satellite TV, an electric kettle, and a safe. Certain rooms offer a private balcony. The en-suite bathrooms have a shower and complimentary toiletries.</p><p>Ibis Styles Bali Benoa is a 25-minute drive from the bustling Kuta area. Ngurah Rai International Airport is located 12 km away from the hotel, which provides airport shuttle service at an additional cost.</p><p>With a 24-hour front desk, the hotel offers baggage storage and currency exchange services. Tour arrangements can be made at the tour desk. Other recreational options include enjoying a massage or relaxing in the sauna. Car rental is available for those who wish to explore the surrounding area.</p><p>You can enjoy international cuisine at The Ocean Restaurant or have drinks at the Splash Pool Bar. In-room dining options are available through room service.</p>', '<p>Wi-Fi is available throughout the hotel and is free of charge.</p>', NULL, 'Active', '1685331791_exterior-view.jpg', 2, 'https://ibisstylesbenoa.com-bali.com/id/', 'https://goo.gl/maps/Wwd2KeRQQEBPW5E29', NULL, NULL, '<p><strong>1. All periods (except peak season):</strong><br />For cancellations received inside 72 hours of arrival, the hotel will apply a charge equivalent to 50% of the contracted rate for the entire stay. For cancellations received inside 24<br />hours of arrival, the hotel will apply a charge equivalent to 100% of the contracted rate for the entire stay. For reservations amendments, which shorten the stay, the same<br />cancellation conditions will apply.<br /><strong>2. Period from (24 Dec&#39;23 - 02 Jan&#39;24, 9 - 24 Feb&#39;24):</strong><br />For cancellations received inside 14 days of arrival, the hotel will apply a charge equivalent to 50% of the contracted rate for the entire stay. For cancellations received inside 7<br />days of arrival the hotel will apply a charge equivalent to 100% of the contracted rate for the entire stay. For reservations amendments which shorten the stay, the same<br />cancellation conditions will apply.</p>', NULL, '2023-05-29 03:43:11', '2023-05-29 04:02:03'),
(100, 'Sofitel Hotel & Resorts', 'pYPl247FEaLmzMwbvhlpSFKTJL', 'Nusa Dua', 'ITDC Lot N5, Nusa Dua, Bali', 'Tri Wahyu Prasetyo', '08116000510', '<p>A lavish and sophisticated beachfront retreat offering the height of tropical luxury. Boasting superior views of the shimmering sea, Sofitel&rsquo;s 415 exquisite rooms, suites and villas offer true five-star comfort. Indulge in a savant mix of chic world-class facilities, French elegance, and authentic Balinese charm.</p>', '<p>-</p>', '<p>Check in time is 15:00 and check out time is 11:00. Early check in (before 15:00), late check-out (up to 14:00), and day use is at the discretion of the hotel and is normally subject to charge at 50% of the room rate (subject to availability). Full Price will normally be charged for check out after 18:00 or check in prior to 09:00.</p><p>Complimentary accommodation and breakfast for 1 child under 12 years old, additional with 1 baby crib or rollaway bed. To guarantee the availability the baby crib/rollaway bed, it shall be booked upon room reservation; otherwise, it is subject to availability. Club access benefits extended to maximum of 1 child.</p>', 'Active', '1685351116_Cover.jpg', 2, 'https://sofitelbalinusadua.com/', 'https://goo.gl/maps/pGooxvuw1X9bsApM9', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-05-29 09:05:16', '2023-05-29 09:09:56'),
(101, 'Jumana Bali Ungasan Resort', 'cb2epqiOA4IXtU4qVPtSK4wINX', 'South Kuta', 'Banjar Kelod, Jl. Melasti, Ungasan, South Kuta, Badung Regency, Bali 80364', 'Yemima Tewuh', '0361710663', '<p>Located 70 metres above the ocean upon the pristine cliffs of southern Bali, Jumana Bali Ungasan Resort is elegantly appointed with a serene ambiance, ideal for your relaxing escape.&nbsp;<br />The pristine limestone cliffside, renowned beach clubs, and tranquil Melasti beach are the perfect pairing to the all-pool villa resorts panoramic surroundings.&nbsp;<br />Experience endless adventures, unforgettable cultural discoveries and discover true relaxation in this charming island resort with distinctive Balinese touches that will tantalize the minds of new and returning visitors alike.</p>', '<p>* Extravagant marble bathroom with bathtub&nbsp;</p><p>* Outdoor swimming pool and jetpool&nbsp;</p><p>* Balinese bale complete with personal daybed&nbsp;</p><p>* Complimentary high speed wireless internet</p>', NULL, 'Active', '1685419868_Cover.jpg', 2, 'https://www.jumanabali.com/', 'https://goo.gl/maps/kK6y9nyBPwUHjktp7', NULL, NULL, '<p><strong>CHILDREN POLICY</strong><br />Maximum of 2 children with accompanying adults. No room charge shall be made for children below 12 years of age and under sharing the same room with their parent(s) or grandparent(s) without request of extra bed although booking an extra bed is strongly recommended. Breakfast and other meals rates will be charge at 50% off adults Meals Rates for children 5- 11.99 years old.<br />Baby Cot is free of charge for infants 0-1.99 years with advance notice when making the booking<br />Complimentary a maximum of one extra bed for children below 12 years old</p><p><strong>CANCELLATION POLICY</strong><br />The Business Partner shall notify the Resort in writing of any cancellation or changes to the confirmed reservations subject to the following: 1. Cancellations received 14 days prior to arrival will be charged at 1-night accommodation including applicable service charge and taxes. 2. Cancellations received within 7 days prior to arrival or No-show or shorten stay will be charged at 100% accommodation including applicable service charge and taxes</p>', NULL, '2023-05-30 04:11:08', '2023-05-30 05:54:53'),
(102, 'K Club Ubud', 'WGpcrnxH7F1wp6ytqT9CRdNdbS', 'Ubud', ':Jalan Raya Cebok , Kedisan Tegallalang, Kedisan, Kecamatan Ubud, Kabupaten Gianyar Bali, 80561', 'Mr. I Wayan Suambara', '08170288899', '<p>K-Club Ubud is composed of 30 fully service villas completely integrated into the environment, with an organic restaurant, a new kind of spa, and an inviting pool club. The fitness and yoga facilities overlook the calm, green jungle.</p><p>Construction on this development began in early 2019 and we have steadily continued throughout the very challenging year of 2020. Interestingly, a new clientele has emerged &ndash; the digital nomads.</p><p>The health crisis has accelerated technology and changed how workspaces are defined. Working remotely has moved from being a growing trend, to a forced reality for many and can now be done from anywhere in the world. People are choosing to work under the sun, calm and safe.</p>', '<p>1. Outdoor Swimming Pool<br />2. Tropical Villa interior with High Ceiling<br />3. Spacious Living Area with Ceiling Fans<br />4. Fully Equipped Kitchen with Bar Counter<br />5. Garden features Swimming Pool with Wooden Deck<br />6. Family size Dining Table<br />7. Smart TV in each room<br />8. Hi-Speed Wi-Fi Connection<br />9. Pantry in the master bedroom<br />10. Refrigerator<br />11. Iron and iron board</p><p>12. 1x Bathtub in each unit or / villa<br />13. Bathroom in each room<br />14. Air conditioning in each room<br />15. Coffee maker<br />16. In-room safe<br />17. Portable speaker</p>', '<p>No pet allowed entering K Club Ubud</p><p><strong>CHECK-IN AND CHECK OUT TIME:</strong><br /> Check-in time is 15:00PM check-out time is 12:00PM<br /> All guests arriving before 15:00 will be accommodated as villas become available.<br /> Baggage may be checked-in for those arriving early if villas are unavailable.<br /> Late check out/day use will be subject to availability.<br /> Check out time until 18:00 hours will be charged 50%.<br /> Check out time after 18:00 hours will be charged 100%.<br /> Late check out will be confirmed by advanced deposit or other arrangements that are approved by<br />the villa</p>', 'Active', '1685514331_K-ClubKabana.jpg', 2, 'https://kclububud.com/', 'https://goo.gl/maps/AbEWAxFxgZBLnzXw8', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-05-31 06:25:31', '2023-05-31 08:00:34'),
(103, 'Natya Resort Ubud', 'EA1AG5EnCcAZ6w9Sk1ZqIiskjs', 'Tegallalang', 'Kelabang Moding, Tegallalang, Kec. Tegallalang, Kabupaten Gianyar, Bali 80571', 'Maya Theresia', '03613007799', '<p>Natya Hotels&rsquo; latest offering is this striking up and coming resort in Ubud, which will treat guests seeking a scenic retreat amidst Bali&rsquo;s verdant and cultural heartland. The resort is located in a pristine valley, located within the rural upland neighborhood of Banjar Kelabang Moding, which is within only a 15-minute transfer to the hub of Ubud town. The secluded area is entered through Jalan Suweta, up north from the Ubud Royal Palace.</p>', '<p>* Outdoor swimming pool</p><p>* Restaurant and bar serving</p><p>* Shuttle Service</p><p>* Airport Pick-up/Drop off</p><p>* Spa &amp; Salon</p><p>* Laundry services</p><p>* Afternoon tea</p><p>* Natys Restaurant</p><p>* 24-hour security on duty</p><p>*&nbsp; CCTV camera</p>', NULL, 'Active', '1685525317_DJI_00555.jpg', 2, 'www.natyahotel.com', 'https://goo.gl/maps/oa2qg7AsvDbon4HB8', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-05-31 09:28:37', '2023-05-31 09:30:46'),
(104, 'Four Season Resort Bali At Sayan', 'rhXp7x2XucweS2PI7bQrUlWLvh', 'Ubud', 'Jl. Raya Sayan, Sayan, Kecamatan Ubud, Kabupaten Gianyar, Bali 80571', 'Elis Tanthra', '0361977577', '<p>Four Seasons Resort Sayan encapsulates Bali at its philosophical and soulful best: a sublime hillside haven where man, humanity and nature unite with purest intent. Only a 10 minute drive from the stylish boutiques, artist ateliers and atmospheric eateries of boho-chic Ubud, Four Seasons Sayan is an inspiring base from which to explore Bali&#39;s cultural heart or to retreat into nature&#39;s meditative embrace. Arrive via a dramatic bridge, beneath which the Ayung River valley spreads its tropical arms. Descend from the gravity-defying rooftop lotus pond to the two-tiered swimming pool cantilevered over the river, through an enchanting forest that cocoons just 60 suites and villas. Choose from secluded treetop accommodations or riverside sanctuaries &ndash; all ultra-comfortable and authentically Balinese, furnished with traditional ikat fabrics, antique furnishings and Indonesian artefacts.</p>', '<p>- Pool Facilities&nbsp;</p><p>- Salon (Open-By Appointment Only)&nbsp;</p><p>- Fitness Centre&nbsp;</p><p>- Spa&nbsp;</p><p>- Local Shuttle / Car Service&nbsp;</p><p>- Airport Transportation&nbsp;</p><p>- Parking &amp; Valet&nbsp;</p><p>- Riverside&nbsp;</p><p>- Ayung Terrace&nbsp;</p><p>- Chef&#39;s Table at Sokasi&nbsp;</p><p>- Jati Bar&nbsp;</p><p>- Kids Club&nbsp;</p><p>- Babysitting Service&nbsp;</p>', '<p>No check out is allowed on 31 Dec 31&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Standard Benefit :&nbsp;</strong></p><p>Daily breakfast&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Children Policy :</strong>&nbsp;</p><p>- Breakfast is complimentary for children 0 to 6 years&nbsp;</p><p>- Baby cot/crib is complimentary&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Honeymooners will get the following benefit :&nbsp;</strong></p><p>- Tropical flower bouquet upon arrival&nbsp;</p><p>- A honeymoon cake&nbsp;</p><p>- Flower petals in the bathub&nbsp;</p>', 'Active', '1686279742_83160592.jpg', 14, 'https://www.fourseasons.com/sayan/', 'https://goo.gl/maps/kas9q9nH2abh7hVp8', NULL, NULL, '<p><strong>Low Season, Shoulder Season and High Season</strong><br />- Cancellations within 14 days prior to arrival will be subject to a cancellation fee equal to one night&#39;s accommodation at the contracted rates, plus applicable taxes and service charge.<br />- Cancellations within 14 days prior to arrival booked under Bali Twice the Magic will be subject to a cancellation fee equal to one night&rsquo;s accommodation at each resort at the contracted rate, plus applicable taxes and service charge.</p><p><strong>Festive Season (24 December 2023 to 02 January 2024 all dates inclusive)</strong><br />- Cancellations within 30 days prior to arrival will be subject to a full night&rsquo;s accommodation booked at the contracted rates, plus applicable taxes and service charge.<br />- Cancellations within 30 days prior to arrival booked under Bali Twice the Magic will be subject to a full night&rsquo;s accommodation booked at the contracted rates, plus applicable taxes and service charge for both resorts.</p><p><strong>No Show Policy for All Suites &amp; Villas Categories</strong><br />A reservation is considered a no show if arrival does not occur on the date reserved. The Resort shall only invoice The Company on behalf of the guest the applicable cancellation charge which a full payment on the nights booked.</p>', NULL, '2023-06-09 03:02:22', '2023-06-22 07:24:44'),
(105, 'Mulia Resort', 'cNAftqTZSsv3KL0hRyl5S84nrT', 'Nusa Dua', 'Jl. Raya Nusa Dua Selatan, Kawasan Sawangan, Benoa Kec. Kuta Selatan Kab. Badung, Bali 80361', 'Yosua Putra', '03618467777', '<p>Discover Luxurious Accomodation in Nusa Dua&nbsp;</p><p>With 526 enchanting guest rooms and suites that are among the largest on the island, our opulent accommodation in Nusa Dua, Bali offers unparalleled comfort and style. Choose from uniquely designed hotel rooms, ideal for couples or families holidaying on the stunning Nusa Dua beachfront.<br /><br />After a long day of exploring Bali, retreat to your room and indulge in our signature plush bedding, luxurious marble bathrooms and high-tech enhancements, all distinctly designed to pamper you. Relax on the spacious balcony as you dwell amongst the beauty of our tranquil surroundings and take in the refreshing sea breeze. Our accommodation options aim to provide unmatched relaxation for every guest of Mulia Resort.</p>', '<p>* Fitnesss Centre&nbsp;</p><p>* ZJ&#39;s Bar, except during special event&nbsp;</p><p>* Array of sport and leisure activities (details to be forwarded separately)&nbsp;</p><p>* Mulia Kidz facility during normal operating hours</p><p>* Internet access&nbsp;</p>', '<p>* Daily Breakfast&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Holiday Special Condition :&nbsp;</strong></p><p>* Festive season : no minimum nights required but check out date is NOT allowed on 31 December 2023&nbsp;</p><p>* Nyepi &quot;Balinese Seclusion Day&quot; : no arrival and departure are allowed on 11 March 2024&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Honeymoon Benefit :&nbsp;</strong></p><p>* In order to receive the following honeymoon amenities (served in room upon arrival), copy of wedding certificate valid up to six months after the wedding date must be emailed upon reservation and presented upon check in.&nbsp;</p><p>* Grandeur/Grandeur Deluxe, Signature Ocean Court &amp; Signature Lagoon Access : Chocolate amenities&nbsp;</p><p>* Royal Suite and above : A bottle of sparkling wine and chocolate amenities&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 'Active', '1687424836_1..jpg', 14, 'www.themulia.com', 'https://goo.gl/maps/51KNCjTdLX49pD9M8', NULL, NULL, '<p><strong>Regular Season :&nbsp;</strong></p><p>* A cancellation fee equivalent up to two room nights for cancelation made less than 72 hours prior to arrival&nbsp;</p><p>* A no show equivalent up to two nights will be charged for each room whereby booking will be cancelled immediately&nbsp;</p><p><strong>High Season :&nbsp;</strong></p><p>* A cancellation fee equivalent up to two room nights for cancellation made less than 14 days prior to arrival&nbsp;</p><p>* A no show fee equivalent to 50% of the total room nights or two nights whichever is greater will be charged for each room whereby booking will be cancelled immediately&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Peak Season :&nbsp;</strong></p><p>* A cancellation within 30 days prior to arrival is charged the full length of stay&nbsp;</p><p>* A cancellation fee equivalent to full length of stay&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Split Seasons :&nbsp;</strong></p><p>* A cancellation that falls into two seasonality, its fee will be defined based on policy of whichever seasons that has greater and longer cancellation policy&nbsp;</p><p>* A no show that falls into two seasonality, its fee will be defined based on policy of whichever seasons that has greater no show charges&nbsp;</p>', NULL, '2023-06-22 10:07:16', '2023-06-26 07:37:30');
